17%2F07%2Faadhar_-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20all%20cyborgs.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarwick.ac.uk%2Ffac%2Farts%2Fenglish%2Fcurrentstudents%2Fundergraduate%2Fmodules%2Ffictionnownarrativemediaandtheoryinthe21stcentury%2Fmanifestly_haraway_----_a_cyborg_manifesto_science_technology_and_socialist-feminism_in_the_....pdf%5C%22%3EDonna%20Haraway%E2%80%99s%20cyborgs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201991%20were%20at%20the%20blurred%20intersection%20of%20%E2%80%98human%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98machine%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20hybrid%20of%20machine%20and%20organism%2C%20creatures%20of%20social%20reality%20and%20fiction%2C%20both%20our%20ontology%20and%20political%2C%20due%20to%20our%20interactions%20with%20technologies.%20In%20time%2C%20however%2C%20we%20have%20become%20more%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1068%2Fa3608_b%5C%22%3Ecyborg%20update%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20amalgamation%20of%20individuals%20and%20data%2C%20of%20databases%20and%20bodies.%20Google%E2%80%99s%20reCAPTCHA%20service%20to%20help%20distinguish%20between%20humans%20and%20bots%20is%20a%20great%20example%20of%20this.%20Our%20humanness%20is%20no%20longer%20presumed%20on%20the%20Internet%20and%20is%20attributed%20to%20us%20through%20the%20performance%20of%20certain%20tasks%20like%20pattern%20recognition%20tests.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Internet%2C%20one%20is%20not%20born%20a%20human%2C%20rather%20one%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomsbury.com%2Fau%2Finhuman-networks-9781501316159%2F%5C%22%3Eattributed%20human%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20computational%20means%20of%20differentiation%20between%20humans%20and%20machines.%20If%20one%20fails%20the%20reCAPTCHA%20test%2C%20one%20is%20excluded%20from%20this%20imagination%20of%20the%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Cradle%20to%20grave%E2%80%99%20databasing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20exaggerated%20account%20of%20this%20cyborg-ian%20reality%20is%20most%20evident%20in%20India%2C%20where%20the%20state%20(colonial%20and%20post-colonial)%20has%20been%20obsessed%20with%20enumerating%20the%20population%20for%20effective%20governance.%20In%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20the%20country%20has%20become%20home%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20biometric%20identification%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar%E2%80%99%20which%20bestows%20over%20a%20billion%20people%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98unique%E2%80%99%2012-digit%20number%20that%20connects%20to%20a%20database%20containing%20their%20biometric%20details%2C%20which%20is%20then%20used%20to%20authenticate%20their%20identity%20for%20claiming%20welfare%20and%20other%20services%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Faadhar-card.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-164870%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20Image.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20originally%20began%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fgovernment_tr_rec%2Fleveraging-the-power-of-jam-jan-dhan-aadhar-and-mobile%2F%5C%22%3E2009%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20enable%20direct%20cash%20transfers%20to%20beneficiaries%2C%20intending%20to%20root%20out%20corruption%20and%20discretionary%20action%2C%20today%2C%20it%20is%20being%20used%20almost%20ubiquitously%20by%20both%20state%20and%20non-state%20entities%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20service%20provision%20and%20entitlements%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20state%20that%20seems%20unable%20to%20govern%20without%20enumerating%20and%20databasing%20its%20population.%20Aadhaar%20has%20become%20a%20key%20part%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meity.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fupload_files%2Fdit%2Ffiles%2FDigital%2520India.pdf%5C%22%3Ecradle%20to%20grave%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20envisioning%20of%20the%20national%20digital%20identity%20project%20within%20the%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalindia.gov.in%2Finfrastructure%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Digital%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20program.%20Maintenance%20of%20accurate%20Aadhaar%20data%20is%20now%20the%20cornerstone%20for%20accessing%20any%20modern%20state%20and%20non-state%20service%2C%20and%20securing%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1950044%5C%22%3Esmooth%20digital%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20data-based%20universe%2C%20the%20citizenry%20is%20imagined%20as%20cyborgs%20with%20unique%20numeric%20identities%2C%20endlessly%20online%2C%20hyper-connected%2C%20digitally%20responsive%20subjects%2C%20represented%20perfectly%20within%20the%20national%20identity%20database%20and%20willing%20to%20be%20verified%20as%20authentic%20at%20any%20instant%20for%20claiming%20any%20state%20welfare.%20The%20creation%20of%20the%20cyborg%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20a%20bad%20thing.%20Blurring%20of%20boundaries%20as%20Haraway%20suggested%2C%20might%20lead%20to%20more%20complex%2C%20heterogenous%20notions%20of%20identity%20and%20feminism.%20But%20the%20trouble%20starts%20when%20the%20cyborg%20becomes%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarwick.ac.uk%2Ffac%2Farts%2Fenglish%2Fcurrentstudents%2Fundergraduate%2Fmodules%2Ffictionnownarrativemediaandtheoryinthe21stcentury%2Fmanifestly_haraway_----_a_cyborg_manifesto_science_technology_and_socialist-feminism_in_the_....pdf%5C%22%3Eillegitimate%20offspring%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20militarism%20and%20patriarchal%20capitalism%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20state%20socialism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20is%20even%20more%20urgent%20in%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20when%20the%20country%20has%20witnessed%20the%20horror%20of%20state-sponsored%20murders%2C%20public%20lynching%20of%20minority%20groups%20and%20progressively%20increasing%20violence.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20extreme%20violence%20since%20May%20this%20year%20due%20to%20clashes%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20tribes%2C%20two%20women%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1053038%2Feveryone-should-know-what-happened-to-us-four-kuki-women-recount-brutal-assaults-they-survived%5C%22%3Esexually%20assaulted%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20paraded%20naked.%20The%20mob%20responsible%20for%20the%20atrocity%20was%20seen%20to%20ask%20the%20women%20for%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20to%20verify%20who%20they%20were.%20When%20they%20failed%20to%20produce%20their%20cards%2C%20they%20were%20dragged%20off%20and%20molested%2C%20because%20the%20men%20did%20not%20believe%20who%20they%20were%20claiming%20to%20be%2C%20without%20the%20production%20of%20the%20card.%20The%20cyborg-ian%20reality%20for%20these%20women%20was%20tied%20up%20in%20the%20enormous%20public%20faith%20in%20this%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-proposal-voter-id-aadhaar%5C%22%3EWhy%20Has%20the%20EC%20Brought%20Back%20the%20Dangerous%20Proposal%20to%20Link%20Voter%20IDs%20With%20Aadhaar%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20a%20Muslim-majority%20district%20in%20Haryana%20witnessed%20communal%20clashes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F7%2Fvengeance-muslim-homes-shops-bulldozed-150-arrested-in-indias-haryana%5C%22%3Ebulldozing%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%20300%20Muslim%20homes%20by%20state%20authorities.%20In%20many%20such%20cases%2C%20despite%20people%20having%20lived%20for%20decades%20in%20the%20area%20and%20possessing%20a%20plethora%20of%20identity%20documents%2C%20including%20voter%20ID%20cards%2C%20ration%20cards%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20cards%2C%20are%20interrogated%2C%20detained%2C%20and%20have%20their%20houses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fnuh-violence-300-families-have-fled-nuh-zila-parishad-member-to-hc-8882995%2F%5C%22%3Edemolished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20state%20authorities%2C%20who%20use%20interrogation%20of%20these%20identity%20documents%20as%20justifiable%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20true%20for%20vulnerable%20communities%20like%20the%20Rohingya%20Muslims%20who%20despite%20featuring%20in%20the%20national%20identity%20database%20legitimately%2C%20since%20Aadhaar%20is%20based%20on%20residency%2C%20and%20not%20citizenship%2C%20are%20routinely%20hauled%20up%20for%20%E2%80%98fraudulently%E2%80%99%20acquiring%20Aadhaar%20cards.%20As%20per%20a%20right-wing%20magazine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opindia.com%2F2023%2F08%2Frohingya-involvement-in-nuh-violence-2-rohingya-muslims-caught-with-aadhar-card-and-other-documents%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20state%20authorities%20intent%20to%20investigate%20the%20process%20by%20which%20over%202%2C000%20Rohingyas%20in%20Haryana%20have%20acquired%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20despite%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20determinacy%20and%20accuracy%2C%20the%20cyborg-ian%20identity%20in%20reality%20is%20not%20an%20incontrovertible%20truth.%20It%20ultimately%20remains%20contestable%20in%20a%20Kafka-esque%20nightmare%20of%20vague%20legality%20and%20administrative%20processes.%20The%20indubitable%20cyborg-ian%20creature%20that%20can%20peacefully%20live%20in%20its%20house%20without%20the%20fear%20of%20its%20home%20being%20razed%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20or%20murdered%2C%20therefore%20rests%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20state%20patronage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105412%2F1-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStones%20and%20bricks%20used%20in%20the%20riots%20can%20be%20seen%20everywhere%20in%20Nuh.%20Photo%3A%20Atul%20Ashok%20Howale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20antithetical%20to%20this%20%E2%80%93%20the%20%E2%80%98ideal%20cyborg%E2%80%99%20then%20must%20be%20the%20inverse%2C%20a%20party%20to%20what%20Haraway%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarwick.ac.uk%2Ffac%2Farts%2Fenglish%2Fcurrentstudents%2Fundergraduate%2Fmodules%2Ffictionnownarrativemediaandtheoryinthe21stcentury%2Fmanifestly_haraway_----_a_cyborg_manifesto_science_technology_and_socialist-feminism_in_the_....pdf%5C%22%3Einformatics%20of%20domination%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20insists%20that%20everyone%20participate%20in%20the%20big%20data%20project%2C%20and%20offer%20up%20all%20data%20generated%20in%20our%20everyday%20lives%20to%20help%20contribute%20to%20scientific%20advancement%2C%20and%20innovation.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20then%20of%20good%20citizens%20to%20assist%20in%20data%20gathering%20and%20collection%2C%20and%20in%20databasing%20attempts%20for%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2Fen%2Fabout-uidai%2Funique-identification-authority-of-india%2Fvision-mission.html%5C%22%3Enation-building%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20encoding%20of%20the%20ideal%20cyborg%20underlies%20most%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20at%20legislating%20databasing%20and%20enumeration%20of%20the%20citizenry%3B%20also%20encoding%20into%20laws%20what%20it%20means%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20country%20today%20as%20a%20less-than-ideal%20cyborg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmpire%20of%20empiricism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20state%E2%80%99s%20obsession%20with%20enumeration%20and%20encoding%20bodies%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20colonial%20India.%20The%20British%20colonial%20government%20pioneered%20in%20adopting%20statistical%20classification%20practices%20to%20map%20%E2%80%98truths%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98facts%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20of%20conquered%20lands%20and%20peoples.%20Over%20time%2C%20this%20method%20of%20historicity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fbook%2F10.1057%2F9781137011923%5C%22%3Eexpanded%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20with%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20British%20Empire.%20The%20formation%20of%20the%20Statistical%20Committee%20in%201862%2C%20the%20Statistical%20Bureau%20in%201895%2C%20and%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20first%20Population%20Census%20in%201881%20and%20then%20again%20in%201891%2C%20are%20all%20examples%20of%20the%20administration%20attempting%20to%20understand%20the%20polity%20in%20numerical%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20colonial%20state%20also%20believed%20in%20the%20scientific%20accuracy%20and%20incontestable%20truth%20of%20numbers.%20This%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fresource%2Fgeneral-report-on-the-census-of-india-1891%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20General%20Census%20of%201891%20which%20stated%20that%20the%20census%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20difficult%20and%20uncontrollable%20factors%20like%20moonlight%20guiding%20the%20census%20officials%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20exercise%2C%20multiple%20religious%20ceremonies%20and%20festivals%20affecting%20the%20exercise%2C%20and%20cultural%2C%20linguistic%20and%20religious%20diversity%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20census%20was%20sometimes%20conducted%20by%20officers%20who%20had%20never%20set%20foot%20in%20those%20provinces.%20Much%20of%20the%20stated%20accuracy%20of%20the%20census%20was%20later%20contested%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F206986%5C%22%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20being%20grossly%20simplified%2C%20inaccurate%2C%20and%20unreliable%2C%20especially%20in%20its%20enumeration%20of%20the%20colonial%20subject%20by%20caste%20and%20ethnicity.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20declare%20January%2011%2C%201931%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianculture.gov.in%2Farchives%2Fboycott-congress-census-1931%5C%22%3ECensus%20Boycott%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20this%20enumerative%20exercise%20was%20severe%2C%20with%20several%20historians%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F14631369.2012.710079%5C%22%3Earguing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20questionable%20classifiers%2C%20and%20tabulation%20attempts%2C%20along%20with%20the%20publication%20of%20data%20caused%20sharp%20communal%20divides%2C%20and%20even%20had%20a%20role%20in%20shaping%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20consciousness%20and%20relationships%20in%20both%20colonial%20and%20post-colonial%20India.%20The%20scientific%20therefore%20bled%20into%20the%20cyborg-ian%20material%20reality%2C%20affecting%20the%20relationship%20between%20religious%20groups%20in%20both%20colonial%20and%20post-colonial%20India.%20Other%20instances%20of%20imperial%20scientific%20methods%20of%20using%20colonialised%20bodies%20as%20sites%20of%20enumeration%20are%20visible%20in%20the%20histories%20of%20DNA%20and%20fingerprinting%2C%20issuance%20of%20identity%20cards%2C%20and%20other%20technologies%20of%20mass%20identification%20and%20surveillance%20in%20several%20post-colonial%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegislating%20databasing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20impulses%20of%20the%20colonial%20state%20to%20assert%20and%20contribute%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F2053951717724477%5C%22%3Epublic%20fact-making%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20what%20it%20claims%20to%20be%20objective%20and%20scientific%20knowledge%20have%20been%20borrowed%20from%2C%20and%20replicated%20to%20a%20large%20extent%20by%20the%20modern%20Indian%20state.%20The%20Aadhaar%20databasing%20project%20in%20modern%20India%20represents%20this%20state-held%20faith%20in%20the%20incontrovertible%20knowledge%20of%20the%20cyborg-ian%20citizen%20perfectly.%20It%20characterises%20both%20the%20interpolation%20of%20data%20with%20the%20human%20(the%20cyborg)%20and%20also%20enables%20the%20interoperability%20of%20this%20data%20across%20multiple%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22562%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Faadhar.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-161394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22284%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20databasing%20function%20of%20Aadhaar%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20adopted%20as%20a%20policy%20imperative%20by%20the%20state%20deliberately%20to%20escape%20the%20spectre%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feref.uni-bayreuth.de%2Fid%2Feprint%2F68650%2F%5C%22%3Epaper%20tigers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20documents%20era%20of%20the%20older%20mode%20of%20state%20and%20statehood.%20As%20such%2C%20citizen%20bodies%20are%20not%20simply%20marked%2C%20but%20laws%20have%20been%20specifically%20promulgated%20to%20enable%20database%20creation%2C%20maintenance%2C%20management%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20monolithic%20labyrinth%20that%20keeps%20connecting%20dispersed%20datasets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20amendment%20made%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meity.gov.in%2Fcontent%2Fdraft-amendments-aadhaar-authentication-good-governance-rules-2020-enable-performance%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20Authentication%20for%20Good%20Governance%20Rules%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20sought%20to%20expand%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20to%20non-state%20entities%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20good%20governance%2C%20and%20to%20promote%20%E2%80%9Cease%20of%20living%20of%20residents%20and%20enabling%20better%20access%20to%20services%20for%20them%E2%80%9D.%20Good%20governance%20and%20ease%20of%20living%20are%20undefined%20terms%20in%20the%20law%2C%20and%20have%20now%20been%20transformed%20into%20gateways%20of%20entry%20for%20any%20prescribed%20entity%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20database.%20Despite%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fcases%2Fputtaswamy-v-union-of-india-constitutionality-of-aadhaar-act-case-background%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOn%2520September%252026th%25202018%252C%2520the%2520Court%2520delivered%2520its%2520judgment.%2Centitlements%252C%2520such%2520as%2520State%2520subsidies.%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%202018%20prohibiting%20the%20use%20of%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20by%20non-state%20actors%2C%20amendments%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20have%20been%20incrementally%20made%20to%20the%20Aadhaar%20Act%2C%202016%20and%20its%20attendant%20Rules%20to%20increasingly%20give%20non-state%20actors%20access%20to%20the%20databasing%20project%2C%20altering%20the%20socio-technical%20imaginations%20of%20the%20database%20and%20the%20impact%20on%20cyborg-ian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Faadhaar-and-my-brush-with-digital-exclusion%5C%22%3EAadhaar%20and%20My%20Brush%20With%20Digital%20Exclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterwards%2C%20in%20August%20of%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20parliament%20enacted%20two%20key%20pieces%20of%20legislation%20which%20further%20expanded%20the%20executive%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20of%20enumeration%20and%20databasing.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Ffiles%2Fbills_acts%2Fbills_parliament%2F2023%2FRegistration%2520of%2520Births%2520and%2520Deaths%2520(Amendment)%2520Bill%2C%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3ERegistration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20In%20perhaps%20in%20its%20most%20expansive%20iteration%2C%20it%20made%20this%20database%20available%20and%20linkable%20to%20databases%20maintained%20by%20other%20state%20authorities%20such%20as%20those%20relating%20to%20population%20registers%2C%20electoral%20rolls%2C%20Aadhaar%20number%2C%20ration%20card%2C%20passport%2C%20driving%20license%2C%20property%20registration%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Csuch%20other%20databases%20at%20the%20National%20level%20as%20may%20be%20notified%E2%80%9D.%20This%20means%20that%20dispersed%20datasets%20can%20now%20be%20connected%20into%20a%20monolithic%20whole%2C%20and%20also%20be%20made%20available%20to%20a%20wider%20set%20of%20state%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpreparation%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmaintenance%E2%80%9D%20of%20these%20databases%20make%20the%20Aadhaar-isation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98economy%E2%80%99%20logic%20abundantly%20evident%2C%20turning%20governance%20into%20a%20mechanistic%2C%20and%20technical%20endeavour.%20As%20citizens%20are%20forced%20to%20submerge%20themselves%2C%20from%20cradle%20to%20grave%20in%20this%20technical%20and%20cyborg-ian%20enumeration%20of%20%E2%80%98governance%E2%80%99%2C%20efficiency%20is%20fully%20quantified%20and%20the%20task%20of%20welfare%20distribution%20is%20reduced%20to%20database%20management.%20The%20amended%20law%20itself%20is%20peppered%20with%20this%20language%20of%20technicality%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Corally%20or%20in%20writing%20with%20signature%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Celectronically%20or%20otherwise%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20even%20the%20%E2%80%98womb%E2%80%99%20being%20metamorphosized%20to%20a%20technical%20component%2C%20distinct%20from%20the%20entity%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunwed%20mother%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20and%20its%20language%20are%20both%20envisioned%20as%20technical%20artefacts%20that%20seek%20to%20enumerate%20each%20birth%20and%20death%2C%20for%20the%20larger%20purpose%20of%20maintaining%20an%20error-proof%20register%20that%20can%20be%20searched%2C%20inspected%2C%20copied%2C%20and%20compiled%20for%20statistical%20reports%2C%20and%20now%2C%20even%20linked%20to%20larger%20unspecified%20purposes%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20ideal%20cyborg%20in%20this%20context%2C%20therefore%2C%20must%20assist%20in%20the%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1950044%5C%22%3Eaccurate%20databases%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20legislative%20act%20was%20the%20promulgation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meity.gov.in%2Fwritereaddata%2Ffiles%2FDigital%2520Personal%2520Data%2520Protection%2520Act%25202023.pdf%5C%22%3EDigital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20law%20without%20wider%20public%20consultation%2C%20and%20passage%20through%20the%20parliament%20in%20what%20can%20only%20be%20called%20a%20democratic%20subterfuge%2C%20the%20position%20of%20the%20cyborg%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20State%20and%20its%20overarching%20powers%20was%20made%20abundantly%20clear.%20The%20law%20is%20tremendously%20expansive%20in%20the%20powers%20it%20affords%20to%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20exceptions%20it%20carves%20out%20for%20the%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20amendments%20made%20to%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Act%2C%201969%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20replicate%20similar%20objectives%20of%20databasing%20and%20enumeration%2C%20by%20allowing%20the%20processing%20of%20pre-existing%20personal%20data%20(for%20the%20state)%20in%20a%20digital%20form%20or%20digitised%20data%20from%20existing%20databases%2C%20registers%2C%20and%20books.%20It%20creates%20exemptions%20for%20the%20law%20for%20non-State%20entities%2C%20particularly%20start-ups%2C%20and%20leaves%20the%20extraction%20and%20use%20of%20personal%20data%20open%20to%20an%20unspecified%20and%20increasing%20number%20of%20actors.%20These%20exemptions%20for%20processing%20of%20data%20are%20even%20extended%20to%20economic%20logics%20of%20ascertaining%20financial%20information%2C%20and%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20of%20persons%20defaulting%20on%20loans%20and%20advances%20taken%20from%20financial%20institutions.%20These%20provisions%20reveal%2C%20more%20acutely%20than%20ever%2C%20how%20the%20implications%20of%20enumeration%20will%20be%20felt%20more%20keenly%20by%20some%20over%20others%3B%20by%20those%20who%20are%20poor%2C%20financially%20oppressed%2C%20and%20marginalised%20than%20the%20rich%3B%20by%20some%20cyborg-ian%20bodies%20over%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20not%20only%20expands%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ability%20for%20enumeration%20and%20databasing%20but%20also%20enables%20it%20by%20weakening%20the%20existing%20safeguards%20against%20State%20abuse.%20It%20creates%20a%20%E2%80%98weak%E2%80%99%20regulatory%20body%20without%20provisions%20for%20independent%20functioning%2C%20and%20relegates%20its%20most%20important%20functions%20to%20future%20executive%20rule-making.%20Further%2C%20it%20cleaves%20open%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20and%20exempts%20the%20state%20from%20any%20accountability%20to%20the%20public%2C%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20information%20relating%20to%20personal%20information.%20In%20the%20form%20and%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20law%20has%20been%20heralded%2C%20the%20few%20existing%20protections%20and%20possibilities%20for%20a%20more%20robust%20data%20protection%20law%20seem%20now%20more%20diminished%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnumeration%20and%20databasing%20of%20the%20cyborg%20therefore%20have%20been%20transformed%20into%20an%20essentialist%20feature%20of%20modern%20technology%20law%20in%20India.%20The%20State%E2%80%99s%20impulse%20to%20database%2C%20to%20hide%20in%20the%20security%20of%20this%20inscription%2C%20and%20to%20revel%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20creationism%20is%20evident%20in%20all%20of%20its%20recent%20legislative%20endeavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-memory%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20piece%20has%20assumed%20that%20enumeration%20and%20databasing%20in%20the%20cyborg-ian%20context%20of%20today%20serve%20no%20larger%20normative%20good.%20This%20assumption%20is%20rooted%20both%20in%20the%20histories%20and%20unfolding%20stories%20of%20severe%20marginalisation%20and%20violence%20in%20India.%20Lives%20of%20the%20enumerated%20are%20not%20just%20easy%20to%20manage%20within%20a%20database%2C%20but%20also%20easy%20to%20discard.%20You%20do%20with%20them%20as%20you%20would%20with%20numbers%20%E2%80%93%20view%20them%20in%20binary%20digits%2C%20count%2C%20subtract%2C%20add%2C%20multiplicate%2C%20delete.%20Close%20attention%20should%20be%20paid%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20both%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Amendment%20and%20the%20Digital%20PDP%20Bill%2C%202023%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20an%20environment%20of%20extreme%20brutality%20and%20violence%2C%20using%20the%20Parliament%20to%20provide%20a%20veneer%20of%20democratic%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31114932%2Fcyber-security-g501a12846_1920.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31114932%2Fcyber-security-g501a12846_1920.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31114932%2Fcyber-security-g501a12846_1920-300x180.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F31114932%2Fcyber-security-g501a12846_1920-1024x614.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665938%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Pete%20Linforth%2FPixabay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20legislative%20acts%20then%20not%20only%20attempt%20to%20detract%20from%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20country%20but%20also%20manifest%20a%20form%20of%20state%20memorialisation.%20This%20is%20reflected%20abundantly%20in%20the%20language%20and%20import%20of%20these%20laws%20as%20being%20pathways%20to%20a%20statistically%20sound%20and%20immutable%20future%20for%20the%20cyborg.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20State%20has%20always%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fijtj%2Farticle%2F14%2F2%2F320%2F5866172%5C%22%3Eofficial%20memory%20entrepreneurship%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20important%20for%20creating%20a%20collective%20story%20of%20unity%2C%20identity%2C%20and%20belonging.%20The%20enumerative%20State%20therefore%20derives%20power%20from%20the%20ability%20to%20control%20memory%20and%20build%20a%20generalised%20narrative%20of%20identification%20and%20effective%20governance.%20The%20ideal%20cyborg%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20collective%20memory%2C%20and%20be%20able%20to%20be%20chosen%20out%20of%20the%20pack%20at%20any%20time%2C%20for%20any%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20attempt%20to%20resist%20this%20particular%20notion%20of%20the%20cyborg-ian%20future%20is%20therefore%20an%20act%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmuse.jhu.edu%2Farticle%2F657331%2Fpdf%5C%22%3Eanti-memory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20kind%20of%20anti-memory%20exercise%20then%20becomes%20a%20way%20to%20punctuate%20the%20officious%20and%20technical%20language%20of%20the%20state%20and%20imbue%20this%20form%20of%20narrativisation%20with%20complexity%2C%20and%20uncertainty.%20The%20enumerative%20state%20can%20only%20be%20countered%20with%20the%20resistance%20against%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20ideal%20cyborg%2C%20and%20the%20ballooning%20of%20the%20database%20can%20only%20be%20impeded%20by%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20multitudes%2C%20not%20the%20simplicity%20of%20a%2012-digit%20unique%20identification%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShohini%20Sengupta%20is%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20at%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%2C%20UNSW%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20an%20Associate%20Professor%20at%20the%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Banking%20%26amp%3B%20Finance%2C%20India.%20Her%20research%20is%20on%20Aadhaar%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20financial%20citizenship%20in%20India.%20She%20tweets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshohinisengupta%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694776452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2Faadhar_-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-enumerative-indian-state-and-the-ideal-cyborg%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20exaggerated%20account%20of%20the%20cyborg-ian%20reality%20is%20most%20evident%20in%20India%2C%20where%20the%20state%20has%20been%20obsessed%20with%20enumerating%20the%20population%20for%20effective%20governance.%20In%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20the%20country%20has%20become%20home%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20biometric%20identification%20programme%20through%20Aadhar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-enumerative-indian-state-and-the-ideal-cyborg%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Irfan%20Pathan%20takes%20a%20hilarious%20dig%20at%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694776427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103691546%2Cimgsize-49624.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Firfan-pathan-takes-a-hilarious-dig-at-pakistan-says-asia-cup-final-wont-be-a-one-sided-affair%2Farticleshow%2F103691460.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Irfan%20Pathan%20often%20comes%20up%20with%20humourous%20posts%20on%20th