Indian%20national%20was%20jailed%20for%2010%20months%20on%20Friday%20for%20biting%20off%20part%20of%20the%20index%20finger%20of%20a%20compatriot%20fellow%20worker%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20in%20Singapore%20during%20a%20brawl%20at%20a%20party%20in%20April%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThangarasu%20Rengasamy%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20an%20excavator%20operator%2C%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20voluntarily%20causing%20grievous%20hurt%20to%20Nagooran%20Balasubramanian's%20left%20index%20finger%2C%20The%20Straits%20Times%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERengasamy%20and%20Balasubramanian%2C%20both%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20lived%20in%20separate%20foreign%20worker%20dormitories%20in%20Kaki%20Bukit%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20Nagooran%2C%2050%2C%20and%20a%20construction%20worker%20Ramamoorthy%20Anantharaj%2C%2033%2C%20were%20drinking%20alcohol%20in%20the%20dormitory%20on%20April%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20intoxicated%20Rengasamy%2C%20who%20was%20seated%20about%205%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20pair%2C%20started%20shouting%20and%20Ramamoorthy%20told%20him%20to%20keep%20his%20volume%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20scuffle%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20pair%20and%20Nagooran%20tried%20to%20separate%20them.%20Deputy%20Public%20Prosecutor%20(DPP)%20Cai%20Chenghan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20struggle%2C%20(Nagooran's)%20left%20index%20finger%20inadvertently%20entered%20the%20accused's%20mouth.%20The%20accused...%20bit%20down%20onto%20the%20victim's%20finger%20forcefully%20and%20did%20not%20let%20go.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20and%20the%20victim%20then%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20with%20the%20accused%20still%20biting%20down%20on%20the%20victim's%20finger%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Singapore%20daily%20quoted%20the%20DPP.%20Ramamoorthy%20tried%20to%20pull%20Rengasamy%20away%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20loosen%20his%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNagooran%2C%20an%20electrical%20engineering%20technician%2C%20finally%20managed%20to%20free%20himself%20a%20few%20seconds%20later%20and%20saw%20that%20his%20finger%20was%20bleeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20alerted%20the%20police%20and%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20severed%20part%20of%20Nagooran's%20finger%20could%20not%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20partial%20amputation%20of%20the%20finger%20and%20was%20told%20that%20he%20needed%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDPP%20Cai%20had%20asked%20for%20Rengasamy%20to%20be%20jailed%20for%20between%2010%20months%20and%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20victim%20will...%20likely%20be%20permanently%20inconvenienced%2C%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20profession%20as%20an%20electrical%20engineering%20technician%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20DPP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20Singapore's%20law%2C%20an%20offender%20can%20be%20jailed%20for%20up%20to%2010%20years%20and%20fined%20or%20caned%20for%20voluntarily%20causing%20grievous%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694776200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fc9cdh8ao_us-prison-generic-us-jail-generic-getty_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-national-jailed-in-singapore-for-biting-off-fellow-workers-finger-4392536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2040-year-old%20Indian%20national%20was%20jailed%20for%2010%20months%20on%20Friday%20for%20biting%20off%20part%20of%20the%20index%20finger%20of%20a%20compatriot%20fellow%20worker%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20in%20Singapore%20during%20a%20brawl%20at%20a%20party%20in%20April%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2