0institution%20as%20a%20shell%20of%20what%20it%20once%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TCPD%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20robust%20political%20data%20centres%20in%20the%20country%20and%20a%20popular%20resource%20for%20journalists%20covering%20elections%20in%20national%20and%20regional%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20this%20year%2C%20its%20Lok%20Dhaba%20dataset%2C%20which%20is%20an%20open%20and%20free%20repository%20of%20Indian%20election%20results%20since%201962%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftrivedi-centre-for-political-datas-lok-dhaba-dataset-wins-international-prize%5C%22%3Ewon%20the%20Lipsett%2FPrzeworski%2FVerba%20Dataset%20Award%3C%2Fa%3E%20given%20by%20the%20American%20Political%20Science%20Association%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprofession%E2%80%99s%20highest%20recognition%20for%20public%20data%20contributions%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20an%20open%20letter%20released%20by%20the%20scientific%20board%20of%20TCPD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20three%20months%20later%2C%20the%20TCPD%E2%80%99s%20existence%20hangs%20in%20suspension%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fashoka-university-trivedi-centre-gilles-verniers%5C%22%3Eamid%20the%20dissolution%20of%20its%20scientific%20board%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20director%20Gilles%20Verniers%20resigning%20from%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20administration%20has%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20merge%20the%20TCPD%E2%80%99s%20data%20with%20another%2C%20larger%20data%20centre%2C%20but%20has%20not%20shared%20any%20details%2C%20either%20publicly%20or%20in%20communication%20with%20TCPD%E2%80%99s%20employees%2C%20on%20how%20the%20Centre%20will%20be%20represented%2C%20or%20how%20it%20will%20function%20within%20this%20larger%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20know%20how%20these%20joint%20ventures%20will%20be%20pursued%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20scientific%20board%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict%20%3C%2Fem%3Eover%20email%2C%20because%20they%20have%20%E2%80%9Cno%20details%E2%80%9D%20of%20this%20new%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20University%20had%20plans%20to%20merge%20TCPD%20into%20a%20new%20centre%20at%20least%20by%20July%2C%20it%20informed%20the%20scientific%20board%20only%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20once%20a%20leading%20institution%20on%20campus%2C%20with%20more%20than%2050%20staff%20and%20interns%20working%20in%20it%2C%20the%20TCPD%20shrunk%20to%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20employees%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Today%2C%20no%20one%20works%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20quiet%20exodus%20of%20staff%20since%20at%20least%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20Happens%20to%20Teachers%20When%20We%20Are%20Asked%20to%20Treat%20the%20Government%20as%20Our%20Only%20Teacher%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fteachers-day-india-government-rss-freedom%5C%22%3EWhat%20Happens%20to%20Teachers%20When%20We%20Are%20Asked%20to%20Treat%20the%20Government%20as%20Our%20Only%20Teacher%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20the%20Centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TCPD%20was%20set%20up%20in%202016%20and%20co-directed%20by%20former%20assistant%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20Gilles%20Verniers%20and%20visiting%20professor%20of%20computer%20science%20Sudheendra%20Hangal%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIgIL3aHYI9o%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%3C%2Fa%3E%20Indian%20political%20and%20governmental%20processes%20better%20through%20data%20and%20enable%20a%20data-driven%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hangal%20stepped%20down%20around%202%20years%20ago%2C%20Verniers%20had%20been%20directing%20it%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20TCPD%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_lZbwd5-7hc%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteam%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2011%20permanent%20staff%20members%20and%2025%20affiliated%20researchers%20with%20three%20Fulbright%20Fellows%20joining%20the%20team%20from%20the%20USA.%20That%20year%2C%20about%2040%20interns%20worked%20with%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there%20is%20no%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%20seven%20years%20of%20operation%2C%20scholars%20at%20TCPD%20have%20produced%2016%20ground-breaking%20datasets%2C%20led%2020%20research%20projects%2C%20organized%2080%20research%20seminars%2C%20published%2020%20research%20papers%20and%20book%20chapters%2C%20and%20organized%20two%20major%20conferences%20on%20computational%20social%20sciences.%20The%20team%20has%20also%20published%20more%20than%20300%20analytical%20articles%20in%20the%20Indian%20press%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fashoka-university-trivedi-centre-gilles-verniers%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20scientific%20board%20(referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98board%E2%80%99%20after%20this).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20at%20least%20five%20TCPD%20employees%20(below%20the%20rank%20of%20faculty)%20have%20been%20looking%20for%20new%20jobs%2C%20are%20working%20elsewhere%20already%2C%20or%20are%20pursuing%20higher%20education%2C%20according%20to%20their%20LinkedIn%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20unusually%2C%20TCPD%20did%20not%20open%20applications%20for%20its%20summer%20internship%20programme%20this%20year.%20The%20last%20monthly%20newsletter%20was%20sent%20out%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20no%20further%20datasets%20have%20been%20released%20since%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Local%20Body%20Elections%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20source%20at%20TCPD%2C%20who%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20there%20were%20murmurs%20of%20the%20TCPD%20undergoing%20major%20structural%20changes%20as%20early%20as%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20abilities%2C%20what%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20is%20that%20TCPD%20will%20continue%20in%20some%20shape%20or%20form.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20that%20shape%20or%20form%20is%20right%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20April%2C%20when%20asked%20whether%20TCPD%20is%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20shut%20down%20or%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ES.Y.%20Quraishi%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20election%20commissioner%20from%202010%20to%202012%2C%20who%20was%20a%20distinguished%20fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20said%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20an%20email%20renewing%20his%20position%20at%20the%20Centre%20this%20year%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20every%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20hold%20meetings%20every%20week%20to%20review%20progress%20on%20our%20projects%20and%20the%20work%20of%20all%20other%20employees.%20But%20the%20last%20meeting%20was%20held%20a%20month%20or%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20Quraishi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerniers%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Edict%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20had%20resigned%20from%20Ashoka%20and%20therefore%20from%20the%20directorship%20of%20TCPD%2C%20effective%20September%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15144151%2FGV-1024x680.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22602%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F