20larger%20data%20centre.%20There%20was%20no%20information%20or%20consultation%20with%20the%20Scientific%20Board%20beyond%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20board%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVerniers%20told%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20board%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fno-norms-violated-says-ashoka-university-in-row-over-its-data-centre-101694543458279.html%5C%22%3Einformed%20about%20changes%20to%20the%20TCPD%E2%80%99s%20structure%20only%20two%20days%20prior%3C%2Fa%3E%20(to%20the%20release%20of%20the%20open%20letter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202021%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbloncampus.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fengineering%2Fashoka-to-have-one-more-data-centre%2Farticle37990565.ece%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20University%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20new%20data%20centre%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdeepdive%20into%20data%20analytics%20and%20focus%20on%20research%20across%20categories%20such%20as%20food%20and%20nutrition%2C%20health%2C%20epidemiology%2C%20malnutrition%2C%20sustainability%20and%20climate%20change.%E2%80%9D%20Funds%20had%20already%20been%20sanctioned%20and%20a%20launch%20was%20expected%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomak%20Raychaudhary%2C%20the%20vice%20chancellor%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSLRR01GTa4A%5C%22%20data-hook%3D%5C%22linkViewer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20convocation%20that%20the%20Centre%20for%20Data%20Science%20and%20Analytics%20(CDSA)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20several%20new%20centres%20in%20the%20pipeline%20to%20be%20launched%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CDSA%20aims%20to%20provide%20data%20services%20for%20all%20data-centric%2