weater-sells-at-auction-for-1-1-million%2Famp_articleshow%2F103689353.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meira%20Paibi%20Leader%20Speaks%20on%20Central%20Forces%2C%20'Puppet%20Govts'%20and%20Allegations%20of%20Abetting%20Rape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145950%2Fnangbi-e1694771180308.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20weeks%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20groups%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20removal%20of%20Indian%20Army%20barricades%20across%20Imphal%20and%20the%20hill%20areas.%20The%20latter%20are%20areas%20now%20exclusively%20inhabited%20by%20Kuki%20community%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20the%20claim%20that%20Meitei%20women%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20the%20vigilante%20activist%20Meira%20Paibis%20%E2%80%93%20were%20trying%20to%20block%20central%20security%20forces%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Pallel%20so%20that%20they%20could%20enter%20Kuki%20areas.%20More%20than%2045%20Meitei%20women%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20Meira%20Paibi%20leaders%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20replacement%20of%20central%20forces%20present%20in%20the%20state%20with%20other%20units%20of%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20135%20days%20that%20Manipur%20has%20seen%20violence%2C%20there%20have%20been%20many%20allegations%20regarding%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20Lourembam%20Nganbi%2C%20a%20Meira%20Paibi%20leader%20and%20president%20of%20the%20AMKIL%20(United%20Mothers%20to%20Protect%20Manipur).%20Nganbi%20is%2070%20years%20old%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibi%20women%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20naked%20protest%20against%20the%20Indian%20Army%20on%20July%2015%2C%202004%2C%20after%20the%20brutal%20rape%20and%20killing%20of%2034-year-old%20Thangjam%20Manorama.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20promises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENganbi%20also%20met%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Manipur%20for%20a%20three-day%20visit%20in%20late%20May%20and%20early%20June.%20Nganbi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Shah%20had%20assured%20the%20Meitei%20community%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20separate%20administration%20and%20separation%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20he%20would%20resolve%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%20within%2010%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Nganbi%20made%20any%20requests%20of%20Shah%2C%20she%20said%20there%20were%20quite%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20asked%20him%20to%20bring%20peace%20to%20Manipur%2C%20to%20stop%20poppy%20cultivation%2C%20to%20stop%20narco-terrorism%2C%20to%20develop%20a%20good%20education%20system%20in%20Manipur%2C%20to%20help%20people%20return%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20cancel%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20%5Bwith%20hill-based%20insurgent%20organisations%5D%2C%20and%20many%20other%20things.%20But%20after%20he%20left%20Imphal%2C%20attacks%20on%20Meitei%20increased%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20he%20encouraged%20Kuki%20to%20attack%20us%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002-300x266.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15150000%2Fsignal-2023-09-15-141822_002-1024x908.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221064%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMera%20Paibis%20outside%20the%20Bishnupur%20DC%20Office%20in%20May.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Accomplices%20in%20a%20number%20of%20rape%20FIRs%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENganbi%20also%20claimed%20that%20Meitei%20people%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Clooted%20in%20Churachandpur%E2%80%9D%20by%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20militants%20who%20were%20under%20the%20SoO%20agreement.%E2%80%9D%20She%20further%20added%20that%20women%20on%20the%20Meitei%20community%20had%20been%20raped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuki%20community%20members%20have%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20Meiteis%20who%20have%20attacked%20Kukis%20disproportionately.%20In%20July%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20Meitei%20mob%20and%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20had%20garnered%20nationwide%20outrage.%20More%20women%20have%20since%20come%20forward%2C%20essaying%20accounts%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeira%20Paibis%E2%80%99%20names%20are%20registered%20as%20accomplices%20in%20a%20number%20of%20first%20information%20reports%20alleging%20rapes%20and%20sexual%20assault%20against%20Kuki%20community%20women.%20From%20their%20historic%20Kangla%20Fort%20protest%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20against%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20to%20this%20point%20in%20time%20where%20many%20have%20alleged%20that%20they%20have%20a%20role%20in%20the%20sexual%20crimes%20perpetrated%20against%20Kuki%20women%2C%20are%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20still%20going%20to%20present%20themselves%20as%20ones%20standing%20for%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20women%3F%20Nangbi%20says%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20against%20everyone%20who%20is%20doing%20wrong%20in%20our%20state%20%E2%80%93%20no%20matter%20which%20ethnicity%20they%20are%20from.%20Two%20Kuki%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20but%20the%20ones%20who%20helped%20them%20survive%20and%20gave%20them%20clothes%20were%20Meira%20Paibis.%20We%20condemn%20such%20instances%2C%20and%20we%20believe%20that%20this%20incident%20should%20be%20investigated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nganbi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20and%20Union%20governments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENganbi%20lives%20around%2030%20km%20away%20from%20Churachandpur%20in%20Bishnupur%20district.%20Since%20May%203%2C%20there%20has%20almost%20been%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20internet%20in%20the%20state.%20Nganbi%20said%20that%20she%20was%20getting%20all%20her%20information%20from%20Churachandpur%20through%20her%20phone.%20She%20is%20critical%20of%20both%20the%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20Manipur%20were%20seeking%20help%20from%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%2C%20but%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20any%20help%20from%20them.%20Instead%2C%20attacks%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20have%20increased.%20We%20ourselves%20are%20helping%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nganbi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Kuki%20community%20members%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20administration%20for%20favouring%20Meiteis%2C%20Nganbi%20is%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%20either.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Manipur%20government%20is%20the%20puppet%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%20They%20do%20what%20the%20Union%20government%20wants%20them%20to%20do.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20silent%20for%20months%20when%20houses%20of%20our%20community%20were%20being%20attacked%20by%20Kuki%20militants%20and%20our%20women%20were%20being%20raped%2C%20only%20spoke%20when%20a%20video%20of%20two%20went%20viral.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20condition%20has%20been%20in%20turmoil%20since%20May%203.%20Meiteis%20had%20felt%20left%20out%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20because%20he%20never%20spoke%20a%20word%20for%20our%20community.%20For%20today%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%20completely%20responsible%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20are%20out%20to%20end%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20the%20Meitei%20community%20has%20alleged%20that%20security%20forces%20have%20helped%20Kuki%20militants%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%20while%20Kuki%20community%20members%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20law%20enforcement%20has%20helped%20Meitei%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3EManipur%20Police%20Files%20FIR%20Against%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20%E2%80%98Allowing%20Kuki%20Militants%20to%20Flee%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20Meira%20Paibis%20against%20the%20central%20security%20forces%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20asks%20Nangbi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20of%20the%202004%20protests%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20had%20raped%20our%20sisters.%20Several%20women%20came%20out%20and%20spoke%2C%20but%20some%20decided%20to%20remain%20silent%20forever%2C%20like%20Rose%20Ningshen%2C%20who%20was%20raped%20by%20BSF%20officers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%204%2C%201974%2C%20Ningshen%20was%20raped%20by%20Border%20Security%20Forces%20officers%2C%20and%20two%20days%20later%2C%20died%20by%20s