%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20hedge-fund%20manager%20Ken%20Griffin%20says%20he%20doesn't%20see%20the%20stock%20market%20rally%20of%202023%20lasting%20for%20much%20longer%20as%20the%20impact%20of%20higher%20interest%20rates%20will%20soon%20hit%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndices%20including%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20Nasdaq%20100%20have%20surged%20about%2017%25%20and%2041%25%20respectively%20this%20year.%20The%20jump%20in%20stocks%20has%20been%20fueled%20by%20an%20AI%20tech%20boom%2C%20and%20hopes%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20may%20soon%20stop%20raising%20interest%20rates%20as%20inflation%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20bit%20anxious%20that%20this%20rally%20can%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Citadel%20CEO%20told%20CNBC's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2023%2F09%2F14%2Fpro-watch-cnbcas-full-interview-with-citadel-founder-ken-griffin.htmlhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2023%2F09%2F14%2Fpro-watch-cnbcas-full-interview-with-citadel-founder-ken-griffin.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSquawk%20on%20the%20Street%26quot%3B%20Thursday.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20one%20of%20the%20big%20drivers%20of%20the%20rally%20has%20been%20...%20just%20the%20frenzy%20over%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20has%20powered%20many%20big%20tech%20stocks.%20I%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20rally%20has%20legs%2C%20I'm%20a%20bit%20anxious%20we're%20in%20the%20seventh%20or%20eighth%20inning%20of%20this%20rally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%20noted%20the%20resilience%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20and%20stock%20market%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Fed%20aggressive%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20over%20the%20past%20year%20%E2%80%93%20but%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20typically%20takes%20two%20years%20for%20borrowing%20cost%20increases%20to%20filter%20through%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20instantaneous%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20has%20already%20raised%20rates%20from%20near-zero%20levels%20to%20upwards%20of%205%25%20since%20early%202022%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20cool%20inflation.%20It's%20tight%20policy%20has%20worked%20in%20taming%20price%20pressures%20from%2040-year%20highs%2C%20yet%20inflation%20remains%20above%20the%20Fed's%20target%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-inflation-economy-cpi-august-data-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3.7%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20annually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20now%20at%20the%20point%20where%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20hikes%20really%20start%20to%20play%20out.%20We're%20seeing%20the%20job%20market%20starting%20to%20weaken%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-ken-griffin-anxious-stock-rally-federal-reserve-rate-hikes-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694771423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63caf11d25e32e00190c86d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcitadel-ken-griffin-anxious-stock-rally-federal-reserve-rate-hikes-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20billionaire%20hedge-fund%20manager%20told%20CNBC%20it%20takes%20two%20years%20for%20the%20impact%20of%20rate%20rises%20to%20kick%20in%2C%20warning%20the%20US%20will%20soon%20feel%20the%20pain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ztayeb%40businessinsider.com%20(Zahra%20Tayeb)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcitadel-ken-griffin-anxious-stock-rally-federal-reserve-rate-hikes-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Successful%20Critical%20Interrogation%20of%20India's%20Justice%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15151528%2Fhammer-620011_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20essays%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findconlawphil.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Indian%20Constitutional%20Law%20and%20philosophy%20blog%2C%20a%20legal%20resource%20that%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20has%20become%20an%20almost%20universal%20reference%20for%20law%20students%2C%20lawyers%2C%20academics%20and%20almost%20anyone%20interested%20in%20legal%20developments.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20constitutional%20bench%20hearings%20are%20streaming%20on%20news%20channels%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20in%20front%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20political%20discourse%20in%20the%20country%2C%20author%20Gautam%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20(in%20this%20book%20and%20otherwise)%20has%20allowed%20us%20entry%20into%20courtrooms%2C%20often%20on%20the%20very%20same%20day%20as%20a%20verdict%2C%20and%20get%20a%20fly%20on%20the%20wall%20view%20of%20the%20wheels%20of%20justice%20turning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20benefited%20from%20the%20blog%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20both%20to%20clarify%20and%20understand%20important%20questions%20of%20law%20as%20well%20as%20to%20use%20as%20a%20source%20of%20research%20and%20analysis%20in%20a%20time%20of%20crisis%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20strikes%20the%20reader%20about%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20writing%20is%20how%20each%20article%20(individual%20blog%20posts%20reproduced%20in%20the%20book%20have%20been%20referred%20to%20as%20articles%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20review)%20breaks%20down%20intricate%20legal%20cases%20and%20principles%2C%20offering%20readers%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20their%20significance%20and%20implications.%20Even%20for%20those%20without%20a%20legal%20background%2C%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20explanations%20are%20enlightening%20and%20allow%20for%20engagement%20with%20both%20the%20process%20and%20the%20substance%20of%20adjudication%20in%20the%20Appellate%20courts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20212px)%2085vw%2C%20212px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316-212x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22212%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316-212x300.png%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15145501%2Fimage-1316.png%20432w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3A%20A%20Decade%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20Courts%20and%20the%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20(HarperCollins%20India%2C%20August%2010%2C%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20to%20this%2C%20the%20sheer%20breadth%20of%20issues%20that%20Bhatia%20has%20managed%20to%20cover%20in%20a%20lucid%20and%20yet%20information%20laden%20prose%20(the%20book%20informs%20you%20that%20the%20posts%20covered%20within%20it%20are%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20blog%20posts)%20is%20remarkable.%20The%20book%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20parts%3A%20rights%2C%20constitutional%20structure%2C%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20each%20article%20covers%20a%20judgment%20(or%20a%20set%20of%20judgments)%20corresponding%20with%20the%20larger%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20part%20is%20the%20heavily%20contested%20terrain%20of%20%E2%80%98rights%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20Bhatia%20takes%20a%20largely%20scathing%20view%20of%20how%20courts%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20have%20responded%20when%20asked%20questions%20about%20personal%20liberty%2C%20citizenship%2C%20the%20demolition%20of%20homes%20among%20many%20others.%20This%20is%20notwithstanding%20some%20notable%20exceptions%20such%20as%20the%20judgments%20for%20reservations%20in%20promotions%2C%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20judgments%20(with%20a%20note%20of%20caution%20on%20how%20the%20principles%20contained%20within%20are%20operationalised%20by%20subsequent%20courts%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20prophetic)%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20overruling%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kaushal%20to%20hold%20that%20members%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20are%20equally%20entitled%20to%20rights%20under%20Part%20III%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20theme%20which%20emerges%20from%20this%20part%2C%20and%20one%20that%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20by%20other%20authors%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20is%20a%20judicial%20roulette%20or%20lottery%E2%80%94%20where%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20liberty%20(or%20the%20lack%20of%20it)%20or%20indeed%20the%20burden%20of%20establishing%20citizenship%20%E2%80%94%20may%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20simple%20chance%20(or%20design)%20of%20which%20bench%20your%20case%20is%20listed%20before.%20This%20may%20be%20an%20unavoidable%20consequence%20of%20a%20court%20with%2032%20sitting%20judges%20(usually%20sitting%20in%20combinations%20of%20two%20or%20three%20judges)%2C%20but%20it%20does%20leave%20room%20to%20desire%20greater%20judicial%20consistency%2C%20especially%20in%20matters%20where%20individual%20citizens%20or%20marginalised%20communities%20have%20approached%20the%20courts%20seeking%20hope%20of%20liberty%20and%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20work%20may%20possibly%20spew%20allegations%20ranging%20from%20it%20being%20borne%20out%20of%20activist%20lawyering%2C%20but%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20Bhatia%20is%20not%20one%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20praise%20of%20judgments%20and%20dissents%20that%20according%20to%20him%20follow%20constitutional%20doctrine%20and%20lead%20to%20expansion%20of%20rights.%20One%20of%20the%20many%20themes%20emerging%20from%20his%20work%20is%20the%20notion%20that%20it%20is%20only%20through%20deliberative%20dialogue%20that%20the%20transformative%20vision%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitution%20makers%20can%20be%20achieved%2C%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20fetter%20this%20dialogue%2C%20rather%20than%20protecting%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20judicial%20apparatus%2C%20in%20fact%20only%20serves%20to%20weaken%20its%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjudiciary-in-the-modi-era-shielding-the-state-and-axing-the-people%5C%22%3EJudiciary%20in%20the%20Modi%20Era%3A%20Shielding%20the%20State%20and%20Leaving%20the%20People%20Vulnerable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20book%20deals%20with%20questions%20of%20federalism%2C%20anti-defection%20laws%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Information.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20fresh%20off%20a%20marathon%2016-day%20hearing%20of%20the%20various%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20power%20and%20procedure%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%3B%20and%20in%20the%20past%20year%20alone%20has%20delivered%20judgments%20regarding%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20power%20over%20administrative%20services%20in%20the%20capital%20status%20of%20the%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%20(%3Cem%3EGovt%20of%20NCT%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20modifying%20the%20process%20of%20appointing%20members%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20(%3Cem%3EAnoop%20Baranwal%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20on%20the%20rift%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20functioning%20of%20the%20governor%20and%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20in%20Maharashtra%20(%3Cem%3ESubhash%20Desai%20v.%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20Governor%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20the%20positions%20of%20law%20enunciated%20in%20%E2%80%98Govt%20of%20NCT%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Anoop%20Baranwal%E2%80%99%20have%20since%20been%20altered%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20through%20the%20introduction%20of%20an%20Ordinance%20and%20a%20Bill%2C%20respectively.%20This%20highlights%20the%20tripartite%20tension%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20consolidation%20of%20power%20in%20the%20Union%20on%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20the%20principle%20of%20separation%20of%20powers%20between%20the%20organs%20of%20government%20as%20well%20as%20between%20Union%20government%20and%20State%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhatia%E2%80%99s%20enunciation%20on%20the%20developments%20in%20judicial%20discourse%20of%20federalism%2C%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20anti-defection%20law%20and%20the%20role%20of%20Fourth%20Branch%20institutions%20are%20a%20crucial%20prism%20through%20which%20we%20should%20view%20these%20recent%20developments%20%E2%80%93%20and%20predict%20the%20manners%20in%20which%20this%20tension%20will%20continue%20to%20prevail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F03163311%2Fgautam-bhatia-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-483348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGautam%20Bhatia%20during%20a%20panel%20discussion%20in%20August%202019.%20Image%3A%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Cem%3EUnsealed%20Covers%3C%2Fem%3E%20lies%20in%20Part%20III%20that%20is%2C%20judiciary.%20This%20section%20focuses%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20an%20institution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20specific%20judges%20(as%20a%20keen%20observer%20may%20glean%20from%20the%20title%20of%20the%20book).%20This%20aspect%20of%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20serves%20as%20a%20radical%20critique%20of%20an%20institution%20that%20though%20so%20central%20to%20the%20democratic%20structure%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20opaque%20in%20its%20functioning%20and%20often%20unwilling%20to%20accept%20rigorous%20public%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20highlights%20various%20instances%20where%20major%20questions%20were%20asked%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20court%2C%20and%20the%20responses%20were%20either%20found%20wanting%20or%20fundamentally%20contrary%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%20His%20articles%20on%20the%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20a%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20enquiry%20was%20conducted%2C%20and%20the%20questionable%20instances%20that%20played%20out%20are%20a%20stark%20indictment.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E..in%20effect%E2%80%A6.damned%20by%20five%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20men%20in%20the%20country%20before%20being%20heard%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20distressing%20legacy%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20that%2C%20the%20articles%20on%20the%20legacy%20of%20individual%20judges%20stand%20out%20as%20fascinating%20insights%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98polyvocal%E2%80%99%20nature%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20progress%20(or%20regress)%20of%20the%20jurisprudence%20of%20different%20strands%20of%20the%20law%20as%20influenced%20by%20specific%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Findia-supreme-court-people-centric-polyvocal-image%5C%22%3EIf%20Supreme%20Court%20Has%20to%20Remain%20People-Centric%2C%20It%20Has%20to%20Shed%20Its%20Polyvocal%20Image%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20obvious%20criticism%20is%20that%20Bhatia%20is%20not%20a%20detached%20observer%20as%20some%20may%20expect%20a%20chronicler%20of%20courts%20to%20be.%20He%20informs%20his%20reader%20of%20his%20involvement%20in%20a%20number%20of%20cases%20that%20he%20writes%20about.%20But%20Bhatia%2C%20unlike%20the%20law%2C%20makes%20no%20bones%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20is%20decidedly%20not%20neutral%20or%20dispassionate.%20I%20would%20also%20further%20argue%20that%20this%20is%20in%20effect%20the%20uniqueness%20of%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20work%20%E2%80%93%20that%20a%20lawyer%20and%20an%20academic%20who%20participated%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%20many%20of%20the%20cases%20he%20writes%20about%20offers%20a%20detailed%20perspective%20that%20the%20brightest%20of%20dispassionate%20and%20uninvolved%20observers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20offer.%20This%20is%20best%20shown%20in%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Privacy%20(%3Cem%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India-%202017%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Section%20377%20(%3Cem%3ENavtej%20Johar%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20Aadhaar%20(%3Cem%3EJustice%20K.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India-%202019%3C%2Fem%3E)%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20various%20instances%2C%20the%20efforts%20of%20Bhatia%20and%20other%20lawyers%20and%20journalists%20to%20critique%20the%20merits%20as%20well%20as%20the%20manner%20of%20functioning%20of%20individual%20cases%20and%20legal%20institutions%20have%20been%20questioned%20as%20contemptuous%20of%20the%20court.%20In%20fact%2C%20Bhatia%20himself%20deals%20with%20one%20such%20instance%20in%20his%20article%20regarding%20the%20curious%20workings%20of%20the%20many%20judges%20hearing%20the%20set%20of%20cases%20regarding%20interpretation%20of%20Section%2024%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act.%20In%20response%2C%20I%20submit%20that%20the%20majesty%20of%20the%20court%20is%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20dealing%20with%20such%20criticism%20and%20is%20in%20fact%20strengthened%20by%20it.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20rigorous%20public%20debate%20about%20the%20merits%20of%20decision%20only%20strengthens%20belief%20in%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20%E2%80%93%20a%20belief%20which%20is%20the%20very%20cornerstone%20on%20which%20rests%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20judiciary.%20Far%20from%20being%20discouraged%2C%20it%20should%20be%20promoted%20and%20celebrated.%20A%20world%20of%20law%20students%20engaging%20in%20debates%20on%20issues%20highlighted%20in%20this%20book%20can%20only%20serve%20as%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20the%20legal%20institutions%2C%20and%20society%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20preface%2C%20the%20author%20states%20that%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20demystify%2C%20democratise%2C%20and%20promote%20engagement%20with%20constitutional%20law.%20His%20work%2C%20in%20this%20book%20and%20beyond%2C%20has%20been%20hugely%20successful%20at%20doing%20so.%20I%20would%20take%20the%20liberty%20of%20adding%20a%20fourth%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20critical%20interrogation%20of%20the%20justice%20system%20of%20our%20nation.%20It%20is%20this%20that%20he%20has%20been%20successful%20at%20in%20challenging%20times%2C%20and%20for%20this%20his%20book%20deserves%20most%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArchit%20Krishna%20is%20a%20lawyer%20practicing%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694771271000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15151528%2Fhammer-620011_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-successful-critical-interrogation-of-indias-justice-system%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Bhatia's%20'Unsealed%20Covers'%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20parts%3A%20rights%2C%20constitutional%20structure%2C%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20each%20article%20covers%20a%20judgment%20(or%20a%20set%20of%20judgments)%20corresponding%20with%20the%20larger%20theme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fa-successful-critical-interrogation-of-indias-justice-system%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foxconn%20founder%20Terry%20Gou%20has%20a%20new%20running%20mate%20%E2%80%94%20an%20actor%20who%20played%20the%20role%20of%20a%20presidential%20candidate%20in%20a%20Netflix%20drama%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226229%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Terry%20Gou%20(left)%20and%20Tammy%20Lai%20(right)%20waving%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Taiwan%20flag.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65040772b8708d0019276f62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFoxconn%20founder%20Terry%20Gou%20has%20picked%20actor%20Tammy%20Lai%20as%20his%20running%20mate%20for%20Taiwan's%20upcoming%20presidential%20election.%3Cp%3EHandout%2FTerry%20Gou%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFoxconn%20founder%20Terry%20Gou%20has%20picked%20an%20actor%20as%20his%20running%20mate%20for%20Taiwan's%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETammy%20Lai%20played%20the%20role%20of%20a%20presidential%20candidate%20in%20a%20Netflix%20hit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGou%2C%20who%20is%20worth%20%247%20billion%2C%20is%20entering%20Taiwan's%20presidential%20race%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECall%20it%20a%20case%20of%20life%20imitating%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fterry-gou-foxconn-hon-hai-founder-taiwan-president-election-2023-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMeet%2520Terry%2520Gou%252C%2520the%252072%2Cbe%2520the%2520president%2520of%2520Taiwan%26amp%3Btext%3DFoxconn%2520founder%2520Terry%2520Gou%2520announced%2Ca%2520global%2520contract%2520manufacturer%2520behemoth.%5C%22%3ETerry%20Gou%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20of%20Foxconn%20%E2%80%94