20consumers%20are%20having%20to%20navigate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20is%20looking%20to%20use%20tools%20like%20AI%20to%20help%20the%20company%20innovate%20and%20roll%20with%20the%20rate%20of%20change%20he%20sees%20in%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20threat%20landscape.%20Johnson%20said%20McAfee%20will%20use%20GenAI%20to%20help%20boost%20worker%20productivity%2C%20to%20help%20with%20things%20like%20marketing%2C%20and%20to%20speed%20up%20how%20fast%20the%20company%20can%20move%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20our%20job%20is%20to%20protect%20customers%20from%20what%20can%20go%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that%20is%20exploding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20cost%20of%20security%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20of%20not%20having%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20stepped%20into%20the%20top%20job%20at%20McAfee%20in%20June%20last%20year%2C%20said%20the%20pandemic%20forced%20so%20many%20of%20us%20online%20for%20work%2C%20school%2C%20and%20so%20much%20else%20that%20security%20became%20a%20big%20need.%20That%20spun%20up%20a%20tailwind%20for%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20one%20that%20wouldn't%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20economy%20began%20its%20reboot%20following%20pandemic%20lockdowns%2C%20the%20burst%20of%20activity%20helped%20fan%20inflation.%20Rising%20prices%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20pushed%20some%20consumers%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20cut%20spending.%20Johnson%20said%20the%20pressures%20some%20customers%20faced%20presented%20a%20challenge%20for%20companies%20like%20McAfee%2C%20which%20in%202021%20sold%20off%20its%20security%20business%20aimed%20at%20companies%20to%20focus%20on%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20late-pandemic%20period%20that%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20potential%20customers%20began%20to%20think%20of%20digital%20security%20measures%20as%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bwant%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20a%20need%2C%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20the%20company%20now%20faces%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20to%20get%20consumers%20to%20reconsider%20the%20threats%20swirling%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20customers%20can%20be%20their%20own%20worst%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20behaviors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20things%20they%20ignore%2C%20the%20things%20they%20explore%2C%20all%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20trying%20to%20lead%20a%20more%20enriching%20life%20%E2%80%94%20can%20paradoxically%20be%20the%20worst%20thing%20they%20can%20do%20that%20causes%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20the%20risks%20that%20GenAI%20will%20help%20churn%20out%20ever%20more%20sophisticated%20scams%2C%20it%20seems%20unlikely%20many%20people%20will%20give%20up%20the%20online%20habits%20they've%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20dual%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20GenAI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20brings%20a%20ton%20of%20benefit%20to%20consumers%20in%20their%20lives.%20But%2C%20paradoxically%2C%20the%20more%20benefit%20it%20brings%20to%20consumers%2C%20it%20also%20goes%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20scammers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcafee-ceo-greg-johnson-cybersecurity-ai-tool-and-threat-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694770561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650323f81afe8f0019ea7907%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcafee-ceo-greg-johnson-cybersecurity-ai-tool-and-threat-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McAfee%20CEO%20Greg%20Johnson%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20cybersecurity%20landscape%20is%20changing%20due%20to%20AI.%20GenAI%20tools%20are%20making%20phishing%20scams%20more%20sophisticated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40insider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A