y%20was%20so%20concerned%20about%20his%20safety%20%E2%80%94%20long%20before%20he%20began%20running%20for%20president%20-%E2%80%94%20that%20he%20hired%20a%20former%20Army%20Ranger%20as%20a%20personal%20security%20guard.%20The%20former%20Ranger%20would%20regularly%20sweep%20the%20Strive%20offices%20for%20security%20threats%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20said.%20(McLaughlin%20said%20the%20security%20is%20necessary%20because%20Ramaswamy%20and%20his%20family%20have%20received%20death%20threats.)%20At%20one%20point%2C%20his%20presidential%20campaign%20employed%20three%20former%20Army%20Rangers%2C%20including%20Ramaswamy's%20current%20body%20man%2C%20according%20to%20financial%20disclosures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Rangers%20were%20also%20responsible%20for%20rushing%20ahead%20of%20him%20to%20his%20hotel%20room%20when%20he%20traveled%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20room%20and%20ensure%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20temperature%26quot%3B%20before%20he%20entered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy's%20campaign%20disputed%20the%20characterization%20of%20him%20as%20entitled%20and%20unusually%20demanding.%20%26quot%3BVivek%20applies%20the%20same%20standards%20to%20himself%20as%20to%20those%20around%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20McLaughlin%20said%2C%20saying%20he%20works%20around%2018%20hours%20a%20day%20%26quot%3Bon%20average%26quot%3B%20and%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Bunusually%20respectful%26quot%3B%20in%20light%20of%20his%20relatively%20rapid%20rise%20to%20immense%20wealth%3A%20Forbes%20estimates%20his%20net%20worth%20at%20around%20%24950%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivek%20doesn't%20believe%20that%20people%20are%20put%20on%20this%20earth%20to%20serve%20him%2C%20but%20that%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20serve%20whatever%20mission%20they've%20signed%20up%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222674%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20grins%20and%20flashes%20the%20V%20sign%20with%20both%20hands%20on%20a%20debate%20stage.%5C%22%20char