ortunities%2C%26quot%3B%20McLaughlin%20said%2C%20characterizing%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20detail-oriented%20than%20ordinary%20CEOs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy's%20latest%20venture%2C%20the%20anti-woke%20asset%20management%20company%20Strive%2C%20was%20kickstarted%20last%20year%20with%20%2420%20million%20from%20investors%20including%20Thiel%2C%20JD%20Vance%2C%20and%20Bill%20Ackman.%20Strive%20passed%20%241%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Roivant%20employees%20said%20Ramaswamy%20worked%20hard%20and%20expected%20the%20same%20of%20others.%C2%A0When%20a%20colleague%20asked%20about%20cutting%20out%20early%20on%20%26quot%3Bsummer%20Fridays%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20town%20hall%20meeting%2C%20Ramaswamy%20ridiculed%20the%20idea%2C%20two%20of%20them%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20lost%20his%20cool%20completely%20and%20went%20off%20on%20a%20rant%20about%20summer%20Fridays%20and%20how%20dare%20anyone%20ask%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20former%20employees%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcLaughlin%20called%20the%20employee's%20recollection%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20Ramaswamy%20%26quot%3Bhas%20never%20once%20raised%20his%20voice%20or%20used%20bad%20language%20with%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.c-span.org%2Fvideo%2Fstandalone%2F%3Fc5081268%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-raps-eminems-lose-yourself%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERoivant%20has%20brought%20several%20drugs%20from%20development%20into%20the%20market%2C%20including%20a%20skin%20cream%20that%20could%20eventually%20generate%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20a%20year%20in%20sales%2C%20the%20threshold%20for%20a%20blockbuster%20treatment%2C%20according%20to%20an%20estimate%20from%20analysts%20at%20Leerink%20Partners%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20if%20FDA%20approval%20comes%20through%20for%20broader%20applications.%20But%20even%20when%20his%20ventures%20failed%2C%20Ramaswamy%20managed%20to%20benefit%20personally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoivant's%20first%20big%20bet%20was%20on%20an%20Alzheimer's%20drug%20it%20bought%20from%20GlaxoSmithKline%20for%20an%20up-front%20cost%20of%20just%20%245%20million.%20Ramaswamy%20spun%20the%20drug's%20promise%20into%20a%20new%20company%2C%20Axovant%2C%20that%20was%20valued%20at%20%242.2%20billion%20shortly%20after%20its%20IPO.%20He%20drummed%20up%20interest%20in%20the%20company%20on%20CNBC's%20Mad%20Money%20and%20in%20business%20magazines.%20Forbes%2C%20which%20had%20named%20him%20to%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fspecial-report%2F2014%2F30-under-30%2Ffinance.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20Under%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%20list%20while%20he%20was%20still%20at%20QVT%2C%20profiled%20him%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20after%20the%20IPO%2C%20poor%20results%20on%20clinical%20studies%20for%20the%20Alzheimer's%20drug%20sent%20Axovant's%20share%20price%20plunging%2095%25%2C%20hurting%20those%20who'd%20bought%20Ramaswamy's%20pitch%20that%20he%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2017%2F01%2F06%2Fthis-millennial-wants-to-build-the-berkshire-hathaway-of-biopharmaceutical-companies-can-he-pull-it-off%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupend%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20by%20liberating%20wonder%20drugs%20from%20the%20greedy%20claws%20of%20Big%20Pharma.%20Ramaswamy%20laid%20off%2067%20people%2C%20trade%20publication%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fiercebiotech.com%2Froivant-lays-off-staff-reassigns-others-major-reshuffle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFierceBiotech%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20employees%20%26quot%3Bthe%20layoffs%20came%20from%20a%20place%20of%20strength%20and%20this%20is%20the%20A-team%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20employee%20recalled%2C%20and%20then%20tossed%20in%20another%20sports%20metaphor%20about%20there%20being%20%26quot%3Bblood%20on%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%20Ramaswamy%20does%20not%20recall%20using%20those%20words%2C%20McLaughlin%20said%2C%20but%20does%20not%20dispute%20the%20employee's%20recollection%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20believer%20in%20cutting%20underperformers%20and%20retaining%20only%20the%20top%20talent%20%E2%80%94%20as%20he%20expects%20to%20do%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22undefined%5C%22%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%94Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20(%40VivekGRamaswamy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1684315227834265600%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20Axovant%20bloodbath%2C%20Ramaswamy's%202015%20tax%20returns%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyale.app.box.com%2Fs%2Fbvv89gcio2tt88j912ktopvqqb3xq2r2%2Ffile%2F1243239079470%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyale.app.box.com%2Fs%2Fbvv89gcio2tt88j912ktopvqqb3xq2r2%2Ffile%2F1243239079470%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eshow%20%2437%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20capital%20gains.%20(McLaughlin%20said%20it%20was%20from%20selling%20%26quot%3Ba%20tiny%20portion%26quot%3B%20of%20Roivant%20stock.)%20He%20made%20%2418.8%20million%20more%20from%202016%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20had%20a%20second%20big%20payday%20in%202020%2C%20after%20Roivant%20struck%20a%20%243%20billion%20deal%20with%20Japan's%20Sumitomo%20Pharma%20Co.%20Ltd.%20Ramaswamy%20reported%20%24174%20million%20in%C2%A0capital%20gains%20the%20year%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRoivant%20did%20better%20under%20Ramaswamy%20than%20most%20similarly-sized%20drug%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Erik%20Gordon%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Michigan%20business%20school%20professor.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20have%20been%20his%20innovative%20approach%20to%20managing%20drug%20development%20or%20luck%20despite%20his%20missteps%20with%20the%20FDA%2C%20and%20probably%20was%20a%20little%20of%20each.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20was%20%26quot%3Bvisionary%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20former%20Roivant%20employee%20said.%20Apart%20from%20his%20prodigious%20ability%20to%20win%20over%20investors%2C%20he%20chose%20a%20strong%20successor%C2%A0before%20stepping%20down%20as%20Roivant's%20CEO%20in%202021%20%26quot%3Bto%20take%20the%20company%20into%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20professionalization%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20deserves%20credit%20for%20all%20those%20things.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20rapping%20at%20the%20Iowa%20State%20Fair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65037377956dba001acdd85c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%20rapping%20Eminem's%20%26quot%3BLose%20Yourself%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Iowa%20State%20Fair.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHype%20man%20in%20chief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20flip%20side%20to%20Ramaswamy's%20ease%20at%20schmoozing%20investors.%20His%20critics%20see%20him%20as%20a%20hype%20man%2C%20wielding%20a%20megawatt%20smile%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAxPNf6XuqM4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edebate%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20rapid-fire%20eloquence%20to%20pump%20the%20value%20of%20the%20two%20companies%20he%20founded%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20his%20presidential%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Roivant%2C%20Ramaswamy%20kept%20his%20politics%20largely%20to%20himself%2C%20former%20employees%20said.%20But%20some%20felt%20his%20political%20ambitions%20were%20obvious.%20While%20he%20worked%20five%20days%20a%20week%20in%20New%20York%20when%20he%20wasn't%20traveling%2C%20he%20maintained%20a%20residence%20in%20Ohio.%20Some%20employees%20thought%20he%20would%20one%20day%20run%20for%20US%20Senate%20there%2C%20as%20his%20friend%20and%20Yale%20Law%20classmate%20Vance%20ended%20up%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20gained%20a%20toehold%20in%20the%20conservative%20movement%20via%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-stakeholders-vs-the-people-11581552372%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal's%20op-ed%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20emerged%20as%20a%20crusader%20against%20the%20environmental%2C%20social%2C%20and%20governance%20(ESG)%20investing%20movement%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20convince%20investors%20to%20put%20their%20money%20in%20environmentally%20and%20socially%20conscious%20enterprises.%20He%20left%20Roivant%20and%20founded%20Strive%20a%20year%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20on%20Ramaswamy's%20tirades%20against%20ESG%2C%20Strive%20promises%20to%20advocate%20loudly%20against%20diversity%20and%20climate%20initiatives%20at%20the%20companies%20where%20it%20invests%20its%20clients'%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20gives%20investors%20the%20option%20to%20put%20their%20money%20into%20exchange-traded%20funds%20(ETF)%20made%20up%20of%20explicitly%20anti-woke%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20in%20the%20fossil%20fuels%20and%20military%20manufacturing%20sectors.%20(Strive's%20biggest%20ETF%20offers%20investors%20broad%20market%20exposure%20to%20the%20largest%20US%20companies.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20ridden%20a%20backlash%20to%20the%20ESG%20movement%20from%20pension%20fund%20managers%20in%20red%20states%2C%20according%20to%20reporting%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levernews.com%2Fhow-dark-money-enabled-vivek-ramaswamys-cash-grab%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Lever%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20nonprofit%20Documented.%20The%20Texas%20Employees%20Retirement%20Fund%20has%20invested%20%24100%20million%20in%20a%20Strive%20ETF%20that%20omits%20Chinese%20companies%2C%20while%20Indiana%20signed%20a%20%24150%2C000%20agreement%20with%20Strive%20to%20review%20the%20state%20retirement%20system's%20investment%20policies.%20Strive%20has%20also%20pitched%20Republican%20political%20institutions%20on%20a%20Strive%20401(k)%2C%20a%20former%20employee%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMcLaughlin%20said%20that%20in%20pitching%20state%20pension%20funds%2C%20Strive%20has%20behaved%20no%20differently%20than%20any%20asset%20manager.%20%26quot%3BThe%20real%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20is%20that%20major%20asset%20managers%20like%20BlackRock%2C%20State%20Street%2C%20and%20Vanguard%20%26quot%3Bhave%20captured%20the%20state%20pension%20fund%20system%20in%20a%20way%20that%20blocks%20out%20new%20entrants%20and%20competitors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20two%20former%20employees%2C%20John%20Phillips%20and%20Joyce%20Rosely%2C%20have%20alleged%20in%20separate%20lawsuits%20that%20Ramaswamy%20asked%20them%20to%20violate%20securities%20laws%20by%20using%20unapproved%20marketing%20materials%20and%20pitching%20investors%20on%20Strive's%20ETFs%20before%20they%20could%20legally%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20suit%2C%20Phillips%20said%20Ramaswamy%20gave%20the%20impression%20he'd%20stay%20involved%20with%20the%20business%20even%20though%20he%20was%20preparing%20to%20run%20for%20president.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20Strive%2C%20Ramaswamy%2C%20and%20co-founder%20Anson%20Frericks%20misled%20him%20about%20commitments%20they'd%20gotten%20from%20investors%2C%20the%20number%20of%20ETFs%20he'd%20have%20to%20sell%2C%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20hire%20more%20employees%20to%20support%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosely%20also%20said%20the%20company's%20HR%20head%20and%20Frericks%20did%20nothing%20to%20investigate%20allegations%20that%20another%20executive%20was%20harassing%20a%20younger%20woman%20employee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Ms.%20Rosely%20brought%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20defendant%20Frericks%2C%20his%20only%20response%20was%20that%20it%20was%20none%20of%20his%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20lawsuit%20said.%20Strive%20has%20disputed%20the%20allegations%20in%20both%20lawsuits%20and%20said%20it%20follows%20the%20law.%20The%20company%20said%20Phillips%20was%20fired%20for%20underperformance%20and%20Rosely%20failed%20to%20meet%20her%20sales%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrive%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20have%20any%20special%20sauce%20except%20its%20anti-ESG%20stance%2C%20two%20experts%20who%20reviewed%20the%20firm's%20offerings%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20basically%20making%20exact%20replicas%20of%20the%20BlackRock%20funds%2C%20but%20they're%20just%20saying%2C%20'Trust%20us%20to%20vote%20just%20for%20profits%20and%20for%20the%20company%20to%20be%20excellent%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20analyst%20Eric%20Balchunas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrive%20said%20its%20management%20fees%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20its%20competitors.%20But%20it%20charges%20slightly%20higher%20fees%20than%20BlackRock%2C%20which%20Todd%20Rosenbluth%2C%20the%20head%20of%20research%20at%20ETF%20data%20company%20VettaFi%2C%20said%20should%20give%20investors%20pause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20%26quot%3Blikely%20not%20be%20eager%20to%20pay%20more%20money%20to%20get%20exposure%20to%20the%20corporate%20efforts%20of%20the%20asset%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenbluth%20said%20%E2%80%94%20something%20which%20holds%20true%20for%20both%20pro%20and%20anti-ESG%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employees%20resented%20being%20pigeonholed%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Banti-ESG%26quot%3B%20investment%20firm%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20Strive%20employee.%20So%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20does%20the%20company%20itself%3A%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said%20Strive%20has%20sought%20to%20position%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bapolitical%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bprioritizing%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Lenzo%2C%20Rosely's%20lawyer%2C%20was%20more%20blunt.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20fairly%20apparent%20that%20the%20company%20was%20established%20merely%20as%20a%20talking%20point%20for%20Ramaswamy's%20presidential%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrive%20dismissed%20talk%20that%20it%20was%20created%20as%20a%20political%20stunt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivek%20was%20under%20no%20obligation%20to%20give%20real-time%20updates%20to%20prospective%20employees%20of%20his%20desire%20to%20serve%20his%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20cheers%20with%20supporters%20at%20the%20Jalapeno%20Pete's%20bar%20at%20the%20Iowa%20State%20Fair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6503b47e956dba001acdf822%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%20cheers%20with%20supporters%20at%20the%20Jalapeno%20Pete's%20bar%20at%20the%20Iowa%20State%20Fair.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20stump%20speech%20that%20works%20as%20a%20sales%20pitch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy's%20run%20for%20president%20can%20appear%20from%20certain%20angles%20to%20be%20the%20sales%20pitch%20of%20a%20lifetime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20stepped%20away%20from%20S