or%20the%20tallest%20living%20male%20dog.%20Zeus%20died%20Tuesday%20morning%20of%20amputation-related%20pneumonia%2C%26quot%3B%20Brittany%20Davis%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20pooch%2C%20told%20GWR.%20She%20added%20that%20Zeus%20died%20with%20its%20head%20in%20her%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20so%20grateful%20for%20the%20time%20we%20had%20with%20Zeus.%20He%20brought%20us%20so%20much%20joy%20and%20happiness%20to%20so%20many%20people.%20He%20will%20be%20deeply%20missed%20by%20our%20entire%20family.%20We%20are%20so%20thankful%20for%20the%20amazing%20team%20of%20humans%20who%20have%20been%20with%20us%20through%20this.%20Zeus%20had%20the%20absolute%20best%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20working%20around%20the%20clock%20to%20help%20him%2C%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20he%20was%20just%20too%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Davis%20believes%20that%20Zeus%20is%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20better%20place%20now%2C%20running%20free%20and%20eating%20the%20good%20stuff%20off%20of%20the%20countertops%20in%20heaven.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMs%20Davis%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgreat-dane-named-zeus-crowned-the-tallest-dog-in-the-world-2951565%5C%22%3Eearlier%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20GWR%20that%20she%20always%20dreamed%20of%20having%20a%20Great%20Dane.%20Luckily%2C%20her%20brother's%20colleague%20bred%20them%20and%20gave%20an%20eight-week-old%20puppy%20to%20her.%20At%20first%2C%20she%20was%20nervous%20about%20having%20such%20a%20large%20dog%20around%20the%20house%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZeus%20used%20to%20prefer%20a%20relaxed%20approach%20to%20life%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20laid%20back%20but%20also%20strong-minded'.%20According%20to%20the%20owner%2C%20the%20dog%20would%20not%20do%20anything%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20do.%20%26quot%3BZeus%20was%20a%20truly%20special%20dog.%20He%20was%20gentle%2C%20l