20real%20terrorists%20are%20those%20sitting%20in%20GHQ%20(army%20headquarters).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20demanded%20an%20end%20to%20the%20terror%20attacks%2C%20the%20release%20of%20the%20illegal%20disappearances%2C%20and%20court%20martial%20of%20army%20officials%20%E2%80%9Cwho%E2%80%99ve%20betrayed%20this%20country%20and%20its%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMazari-Hazir%20then%20chanted%20the%20slogan%20popularised%20by%20PTM%20that%20has%20got%20many%20arrested%20before%20her%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EYeh%20jo%20dehshat-gardi%20hai%2C%20uss%20k%20peechay%20wardi%20hai!%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(Behind%20this%20terrorism%20is%20the%20military%20uniform).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20%E2%80%9Cshown%20major%20bravery%20in%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20she%20believes%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Syed.%20But%20%E2%80%9Clawyers%20and%20journalists%20have%20to%20be%20smart%20and%20not%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20any%20pitfalls.%20Going%20down%20the%20suicide%20route%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20most%20sensible%20move%20to%20make.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArticle%2019%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Constitution%20upholds%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20with%20due%20recognition%20to%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20the%20integrity%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20military%20establishment%20manoeuvres%20the%20political%20game%20for%20their%20own%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jahangir.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20commit%20a%20crime%20%E2%80%9Cand%20then%20expect%20people%20not%20to%20criticise%20you%E2%80%9D%20and%20demand%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20slogans%20should%20be%20according%20to%20your%20taste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20out%20of%20this%20quagmire%20is%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20a%20democratic%20dispensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20the%20army%20should%20return%20to%20the%20barracks%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20not%20interfere%20in%20politics.%20Her%20words%20echo%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1349491%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estance%20consistently%20taken%20by%20her%20late%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20iconic%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20Asma%20Jahangir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-embed-handler%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20excerpt%20from%20BBC%20Urdu%20interview%20of%20late%20lawyer%20Asma%20Jahangir%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20a%20caretaker%20setup%20governing%20Pakistan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20initially%20propped%20Khan%20up%20as%20one%20of%20those%20%E2%80%98projects%E2%80%99%2C%20those%20at%20the%20helm%20now%20seem%20determined%20to%20keep%20him%20away%20from%20the%20political%20process.%20They%20have%20also%20tried%20to%20manipulate%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20and%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(PML-N)%20but%20might%20not%20succeed%20as%20easily%20given%20these%20parties%E2%80%99%20longer%20track%20record%20in%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhichever%20party%20or%20alliance%20comes%20to%20power%20after%20elections%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20within%20this%20year%2C%20the%20powers%20behind%20the%20scenes%20and%20the%20ongoing%20human%20rights%20violations%20are%20unlikely%20to%20change%20much%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbdullah%20Zahid%20is%20an%20aspiring%20journalist%20studying%20mass%20communication%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Karachi.%20Follow%20him%20on%20X%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabdullahhzahid%3Fs%3D21%26t%3DYib5Dr6ZPTJCb9WElKcEJQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40AbdullahZahid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3