20this%20point%20of%20view%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2014).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20being%20questioned%20in%20this%20appeal%20is%20primarily%20a%20policy%20decision%20of%20the%20administration%20and%20no%20breach%20of%20any%20legal%20provision%20has%20been%20pointed%20out.%20It%20is%20not%20within%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20domain%20to%20decide%20as%20to%20what%20would%20be%20the%20choice%20of%20food%20for%20children%20of%20a%20particular%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-lakshadweep-mid-day-meal-237782%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20their%20order%20as%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20will%20have%20to%20accept%20the%20administrative%20decision%20unless%20some%20outstanding%20arbitrariness%20is%20pointed%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20counsel%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20I.H.%20Syed%2C%20said%20during%20the%20hearing%20that%20the%20new%20food%20items%20%E2%80%93%20among%20which%20are%20fruits%20and%20dry%20fruits%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20culturally%20acceptable%20to%20Lakshadweep%E2%80%99s%20people%2C%20Justice%20Trivedi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-lakshadweep-decision-remove-meat-mid-day-meals-schools-dairy-farms%5C%22%3Easked%20if%20%E2%80%9Cdry%20fruits%20%5Bwere%20not%20liked%5D%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bose%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20after%20passing%20the%20order%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20cannot%20import%20personal%20preferences%20in%20policy%20matters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lakshadweep%20administration%E2%80%99s%20decisions%20have%20been%20criticised%20for%20not%20involving%20enough%20consultation%20with%20the%20islands%E2%80%99%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOmesh%20Saigal%2C%20a%20former%20administrator%20of%20the%20island%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20while%20a%20ban%20on%20bovine%