females-older-than-28-can-now-participate-in-miss-universe-a-game-changing-move-for-pageants-4391904%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20Tests%20Emergency%20Alert%20System%3A%20A%20Guide%20For%20Android%20Users%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Telecom%20on%20Friday%20a%20pan-India%20emergency%20alert%20on%20mobile%20phones.%20The%20popup%20alert%2C%20received%20mostly%20by%20Android%20users%2C%20contains%20a%20test%20message%20that%20informs%20the%20users%20about%20the%20government's%20initiative.%20The%20text%20of%20the%20message%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20SAMPLE%20TESTING%20MESSAGE%20sent%20through%20Cell%20Broadcasting%20System%20by%20Department%20of%20Telecommunication%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%20Please%20ignore%20this%20message%20as%20no%20action%20is%20required%20from%20your%20end.%20This%20message%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20TEST%20Pan-India%20Emergency%20Alert%20System%20being%20implemented%20by%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority.%20It%20aims%20to%20enhance%20public%20safety%20and%20provide%20timely%20alerts%20during%20emergencies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20message%20that%20surprised%20many%20users%20is%20the%20government's%20way%20to%20test%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Femergency-alert-severe-explained-received-an-emergency-alert-on-your-phone-today-heres-what-it-means-4305083%5C%22%3Eemergency%20cell%20broadcast%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%20by%20Centre%20for%20Development%20of%20Telematics%20(C-DOT).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F92at5a1c_emergency-test-alert_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20a%20good%20initiative%20on%20part%20of%20the%20government%2C%20here's%20how%20Android%20users%20can%20activate%20the%20safety%20feature%20on%20their%20phones%20for%20alerting%20their%20contacts%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20Google%20Pixel%20phones%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20offers%20the%20personal%20safety%20application%20that%20saves%20and%20shares%20your%20emergency%20information.%20It%20also%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20contact%20emergency%20services%20automatically%20in%20some%20countries%20and%20regions%20and%20with%20certain%20carriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Google%20Play%20Store%2C%20the%20description%20of%20the%20application%20says%20it%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20you%20prepare%20and%20react%20in%20an%20emergency%20by%20quickly%20connecting%20you%20with%20the%20help%20and%20information%20you%20need%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20allows%20the%20users%20to%20send%20emergency%20SOS%20by%20pressing%20the%20Power%20button%20quickly%205%20times%20or%20more.%20It%20also%20allows%20users%20to%20share%20their%20location%2C%20current%20activities%2C%20device%20specifics%20and%20places%20with%20emergency%20contacts%20listed%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20app%20works%20on%20Android%2012%20and%20later%20operating%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20other%20Android%20users%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20users%20can%20find%20the%20option%20in%20settings%2C%20either%20as%20Safety%20or%20Safety%20and%20Emergency.%20Users%20can%20fill%20in%20contacts%20who%20they%20want%20to%20be%20informed%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20also%20has%20an%20option%20to%20enter%20medical%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20picks%20up%20your%20phone%20can%20view%20your%20lock%20screen%20message%20and%20emergency%20information%20even%20if%20your%20phone%20is%20locked%20and%20the%20option%20is%20enabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20location%20service%20and%20emergency%20SOS%20can%20be%20switched%20on%20to%20allow%20others%20to%20detect%20the%20location%20of%20your%