C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENiccolo%20Machiavelli%2C%20had%20he%20seen%20the%20new%20Indian%20blockbuster%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Soldier)%20taking%20the%20world%20by%20storm%2C%20would%20be%20delighted%20that%20his%20key%20idea%20%E2%80%93%20of%20active%20citizenship%20in%20a%20republic%20%E2%80%93%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20it.%20Machiavelli%2C%20admirer%20of%20Greeks%20and%20Romans%2C%20was%20convinced%20that%20citizens%20need%20to%20remain%20continually%20active%20and%20vigilant%20between%20the%20times%20they%20vote.%20Without%20this%20alertness%20and%20engagement%20in%20civic%20matters%2C%20there%20could%20be%20no%20enduring%20republic%2C%20and%20without%20such%20republican%20values%20there%20could%20be%20no%20true%20democracy.%20The%20American%20founding%20fathers%20took%20that%20lesson%20to%20heart%20well%2C%20as%20did%20the%20Indians%20when%20they%20named%20India%20a%20Democratic%20Republic.%20And%20in%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20movie%20star%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20(SRK)%20charismatically%20conveys%20this%20simple%20but%20powerful%20political%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpressinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fjawan-smashes-records-rakes-in-500-crore-worldwide-in-just-4-days%2F%5C%22%3Egrossed%20%2460%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20first%20four%20days%20alone%2C%20the%20film%20presents%20Khan%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20his%20multiple%20avatars%20as%20the%20ultimate%20avenger%20of%20justice%2C%20humiliating%20ill-informed%20ministers%2C%20exposing%20corrupt%20and%20inefficient%20governments%20and%20crony%20capitalists%2C%20redistributing%20money%20to%20the%20most%20vulnerable%2C%20discussing%20agrarian%20distress%20and%20getting%20justice%20for%20those%20punished%20for%20speaking%20the%20truth.%20He%20does%20all%20this%20with%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20charm%20and%20athleticism%2C%20becoming%20a%20hero%20of%20the%20masses%20in%20the%20film%20and%20in%20the%20theatres.%20He%20educates%20people%20about%20the%20stark%20inequalities%20that%20they%20choose%20not%20to%20notice%2C%20while%20thrilling%20them%20by%20outwitting%20the%20baddies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20the%20Fine%20Art%20of%20Managing%20Contradictions%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-the-fine-art-of-managing-contradictions%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20the%20Fine%20Art%20of%20Managing%20Contradictions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20stylistic%20mash-up%20cinematically%20with%20over%20the%20top%20action%20sequences%2C%20romantic%20ballads%20and%20multiple%20roles%20for%20the%20hero.%20But%20that%20is%20to%20miss%20its%20real%20draw%2C%20which%20is%20the%20link%20to%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20own%20recent%20life.%20King%20Khan%20to%20his%20enormous%20fan%20base%2C%20he%20is%20the%20only%20star%20whose%20off-screen%20persona%20is%20as%20admired%20as%20the%20heroes%20he%20plays.%20But%20he%20is%20Muslim%20and%20lives%20in%20India%20where%20the%20dominant%20ideology%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20government%20is%20%E2%80%98Hindutva%E2%80%99%20or%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%2C%20in%20a%20flagrant%20disregard%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20commitment%20to%20religious%20diversity.%20Some%20years%20ago%2C%20Shah%20Rukh%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-34707247%5C%22%3Emildly%20critical%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20new%20vulnerability%20of%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%20and%20for%20that%20he%20faced%20a%20virulent%20attack%20by%20right-wing%20trolls%20and%20his%20films%20faced%20boycott.%20He%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20made%20a%20political%20statement%20since%2C%20to%20the%20frustration%20of%20those%20who%20want%20all%20those%20in%20the%20public%20eye%20to%20take%20a%20stand.%20But%20despite%20his%20restraint%2C%20two%20years%20ago%20a%20government%20agency%20jailed%20his%20son%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fncb-drops-drugs-case-against-aryan-khan-five-others-says-lack-of-sufficient-evidence%5C%22%3Ewithout%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20drugs%20they%20said%20he%20had%20carried.%20SRK%20is%20a%20doting%20father%20and%20talks%20of%20his%20children%20often.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20the%20government%20decided%20that%20punishing%20the%20most%20famous%20Indian%20Muslim%20by%20hitting%20him%20where%20it%20would%20hurt%20most%20would%20demonstrate%20their%20supremacy%20nicely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20400px)%2085vw%2C%20400px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F03150919%2F86722463-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-555735%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Aryan%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESRK%20and%20his%20wife%20maintained%20a%20dignified%20silence%20through%20the%20ordeal%20but%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20outpouring%20of%20sympathy%20for%20them.%20Social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20anecdotes%20of%20his%20endless%20acts%20of%20kindness%20and%20plain%20decency%20over%20the%20years%20to%20technicians%2C%20junior%20journalists%2C%20younger%20colleagues%20and%20ordinary%20people.%20Women%20noted%20his%20impeccable%20chivalry%20even%20when%20no%20one%20was%20looking.%20Everyone%20praised%20his%20ready%20wit%20and%20intelligence.%20All%20agreed%20the%20arrest%20of%20his%20son%20was%20politically%20motivated.%20His%20lawyers%20did%20manage%20to%20have%20the%20young%20man%20released%20and%20the%20charges%20were%20dropped%20this%20year%20because%20of%20the%20complete%20lack%20of%20evidence.%20In%20response%2C%20rather%20than%20make%20a%20statement%20and%20again%20jeopardise%20a%20film%20that%20supports%20thousands%20of%20livelihoods%2C%20SRK%20did%20what%20he%20does%20best%20and%20%3Cem%3EJawan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20the%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinutes%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20film%2C%20before%20the%20audience%20walks%20away%20and%20their%20suspension%20of%20disbelief%20ends%2C%20SRK%20appears%20on%20the%20screen%20alone%20and%20talks%20directly%20to%20camera.%20Holding%20each%20viewer%20in%20his%20gaze%2C%20he%20chastises%20us%20for%20asking%20more%20questions%20about%20whether%20a%20laundry%20powder%20works%20than%20of%20the%20governments%20we%20elect.%20He%20reminds%20and%20admonishes%20the%20audience%20that%20they%2C%20the%20ordinary%20citizens%2C%20need%20to%20recognise%20they%20are%20the%20real%20superheroes%2C%20for%20they%20live%20in%20democracies%20and%20possess%20the%20vote%20which%20is%20their%20ultimate%20superpower.%20%E2%80%98Choose%20wisely%E2%80%99%20he%20tells%20them%20%E2%80%93%20and%20once%20you%20have%2C%20keep%20asking%20questions.%20His%20unmistakable%20political%20message%2C%20like%20Machiavelli%2C%20is%20that%20democracy%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20left%20to%20politicians%20without%20the%20constant%20vigilance%20of%20%E2%80%98active%20citizens%E2%80%99.%20The%20film%20is%20Indian%2C%20but%20this%20message%20is%20true%20for%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22SRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsrk-i-hear-you-and-so-does-everyone-else%5C%22%3ESRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMessage%20delivered%2C%20he%20goes%20back%20to%20one%20last%20breath-taking%20stunt%20in%20this%20high%20octane%20hugely%20fun%20film.%20The%20reaction%20to%20the%20film%20has%20been%20bonkers.%20SRK%20Fan%20Clubs%20have%20organised%20huge%20bann