20became%20a%20full-blown%20riot.%20The%20mob%2C%20comprising%20Hindu%20men%20from%20Pursesavali%20and%20neighbouring%20villages%20of%20Thorvewadi%20NV%20and%20Wadgaon%20Jairam%20Swami%2C%20converged%20around%208%20pm%20in%20the%20village%20and%20began%20ransacking%20houses%20and%20commercial%20units%20belonging%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty-two-year-old%20Nurul%20Hasan%20Shikalgar%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20a%20man%20who%20ran%20a%20local%20earthmover%2C%20was%20among%20the%20Muslim%20men%20at%20the%20mosque%20gathered%20to%20offer%20the%20Isha%20(day%E2%80%99s%20last)%20Namaz.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mob%20had%20sticks%20and%20stones%20in%20their%20hands.%20The%20mosque%20doors%20were%20shut%20but%20they%20applied%20forced%20and%20entered%20the%20space.%20They%20hit%20us%20with%20sharp%20objects%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%2026-year-old%20man%20who%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20to%20his%20head%20and%20has%20been%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20local%20hospital.%20Shikalgar%20too%20was%20hit%20on%20his%20head%20many%20times.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20we%20could%20offer%20him%20help%2C%20Nurul%20had%20died%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20339px)%2085vw%2C%20339px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22339%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X.jpeg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X-249x300.jpeg%20249w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673153%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENurul%20Hasan%20Shikalgar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EShikalgar%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20Shiraj%20confirmed%20that%20by%20the%20time%20they%20found%20the%20young%20man%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20it%20was%20lying%20%E2%80%9Clifeless%E2%80%9D%20without%20a%20pulse%20or%20heartbeat.%20Shikalgar%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%20the%20local%20Krishna%20Charitable%20Trust%20Hospital%20in%20Satara.%20Disturbed%20by%20Shikalgar%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20his%20family%20and%20other%20community%20members%20gathered%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20refused%20to%20move%20the%20body%20for%20cremation%20till%20the%20time%20police%20arrested%20the%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20rumours%20were%20spread%2C%20especially%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20that%20Shikalgar%20had%20a%20role%20in%20posting%20objectionable%20posts%20on%20Shivaji.%20But%20a%20senior%20policeman%2C%20privy%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Shikalgar%20had%20absolutely%20no%20role%20in%20this.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20looked%20into%20things%20and%20can%20confirm%20he%20just%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20mob%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShikalgar%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20educated%20Muslim%20men%20from%20Pusesavali%20village.%20In%20a%20village%20of%20over%201%2C300%20families%2C%20less%20than%2010%25%20belong%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Most%20of%20them%20run%20the%20local%20village%20businesses%2C%20like%20retail%20stores%20and%20automobile%20spare%20parts%20shops.%20Shikalgar%E2%80%99s%20father%20Liyaqat%20teaches%20at%20a%20local%20Urdu%20school.%20His%20mother%20worked%20as%20a%20nurse%20at%20a%20local%20government%20hospital%20and%20only%20recently%20retired.%C2%A0%20Shikagar%20was%20married%20for%20less%20than%20a%20year%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Ayesha%2C%20is%20five%20months%20pregnant.%20The%20couple%20were%20expecting%20their%20first%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Pusesavali%20village%20was%20not%20a%20sudden%20incident.%20Tension%20was%20building%20up%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20villagers%20say.%20The%20police%20too%20confirm%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Canticipated%20the%20worst%E2%80%9D.%20The%20first%20inflammatory%20post%2C%20allegedly%20against%20a%20Hindu%20goddess%2C%20first%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20on%20August%2015.%20This%20post%2C%20allegedly%20put%20up%20by%20a%20young%20man%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20was%20soon%20taken%20down%20and%20the%20police%20had%20arrested%20the%20person.%20He%20was%20let%20off%20on%20bail%20eventually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20incident%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20had%20approached%20the%20police.%20In%20the%20representation%2C%20Muslims%20claimed%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cfeared%20for%20their%20life%E2%80%9D.%20A%20senior%20policeman%2C%20privy%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20confirmed%20having%20received%20a%20letter.%20An%20officer%20said%2C%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20the%20letter%20the%20men%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20threat%20to%20their%20lives%20from%20the%20Hindus.%20It%20was%20a%20generic%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20community%E2%80%99s%20fears%20came%20true%20on%20September%209.%20Locals%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20that%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20mob%20had%20gathered%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20sudden%20provocation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20preparedness%20with%20which%20they%20came%20looked%20as%20if%20it%20were%20a%20pre-planned%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20youth%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20whose%20shop%20was%20one%20of%20those%20destroyed%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20police%20officer%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20post%20was%20seen%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20person%20allegedly%20responsible%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ascertaining%20his%20involvement%20and%20were%20questioning%20him.%20The%20attackers%20meanwhile%20barged%20int