%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20Wednesday%2C%20journalists%20covering%20the%20violence%20on%20ground%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20nearby%20Pune%20district%20to%20file%20their%20stories.%20Even%20access%20to%20Pusesavali%20village%20was%20denied%2C%20making%20ground%20reporting%20that%20much%20harder.%20Santosh%20Shirale%2C%20the%20district%20correspondent%20with%20the%20online%20section%20of%20%3Cem%3EMaharashtra%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20he%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20contacts%20to%20relay%20information.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20two%20days%2C%20I%20just%20could%20not%20file%20any%20reports.%20And%20finally%2C%20when%20I%20managed%20to%20gather%20credible%20information%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20I%20travelled%20almost%20till%20Pune%20to%20send%20my%20story%20to%20the%20editors%20in%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shirale%20said.%20Since%20Pusesavali%20continued%20to%20be%20inaccessible%2C%20Shirale%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20ascertain%20the%20actual%20impact%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20internet%20was%20restored%20on%20September%2014%2C%20the%20police%20say%20they%20closely%20monitored%20social%20media%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20untoward%20activity%20was%20seen%20through%20the%20day%3B%20the%20district%20remained%20calm%20and%20people%20were%20waiting%20to%20resume%20their%20daily%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20policeman%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20the%20local%20administration%20also%20applied%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20CrPC%20prohibiting%20public%20gatherings.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deter%20Hindutva%20leaders%20from%20making%20provocative%20statements.%20After%20local%20BJP%20leader%20Vikram%20Pavaskar%E2%80%99s%20name%20began%20making%20the%20rounds%20as%20a%20person%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20attack%2C%20radical%20Hindu%20organisations%20said%20they%20would%20demonstrate%20publicly%20if%20Pavaskar%20was%20%E2%80%9Cwrongly%20implicated%E2%80%9D.%20Pawaskar%E