20that%20as%20yet%20the%20report%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20conclusive%E2%80%9D%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20distance%20between%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20persuasive%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20conclusive%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20covered%20by%20a%20thorough%20and%20diligent%20investigation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20a%2030-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%2C%20Damodaran%2C%20who%20is%20at%20present%20the%20director%20of%20companies%20such%20as%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%2C%20Hero%20MotoCorp%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20CRISIL%20and%20Biocon%20and%20non-executive%20chairman%20of%20IndiGo%2C%20said%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation%20and%20it%20must%20be%20done%20quickly%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHe%20added%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20if%20not%20all%20elements%20(of%C2%A0the%20%3C%2Fem%3EFinancial%20Times%3Cem%3E%C2%A0story)%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20On%20the%2031st%20of%20August%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20arguably%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20known%20and%20most%20highly%20regarded%20financial%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20published%20a%20story%20raising%20worrying%20questions%20and%20disturbing%20allegations%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20That%20story%20simply%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20got%20the%20attention%20it%20deserves%20in%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20types%20of%20issues%20were%20raised%3A%20first%2C%20are%20the%20total%20shareholdings%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20promoters%20of%20the%20group%2C%20above%20SEBI%20%5BSecurities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%5D%20stipulations%3F%20Secondly%2C%20if%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20does%20it%20suggest%20share%20price%20manipulation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoining%20me%20to%20discuss%20the%20allegations%20and%20the%20credibility%20with%20which%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20made%2C%20and%20what%20SEBI%20and%20the%20government%20should%20do%20in%20response%2C%20is%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20SEBI%2C%20M.%20Damodaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Damodaran%2C%20as%20I%20said%20in%20that%20introduction%2C%20an%20article%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%2031st%20of%20August%20based%20on%20documents%20shared%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20has%20once%20again%20raised%20disturbing%20questions%20and%20allegations%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20reveals%20that%20two%20men%20%E2%80%93%20Nasir%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20of%20the%20UAE%20and%20Chang%20Chung%20Ling%20of%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20spent%20years%20trading%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20Adani%20stock.%20The%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20describes%20them%20as%20associates%20of%20Vinod%20Adani%20and%20says%20their%20investments%20were%20overseen%20by%20a%20Vinod%20Adani%20employee.%20The%20paper%20says%20this%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20they%20are%20frontmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20read%20these%20reports%2C%20so%20can%20I%20start%20by%20asking%20how%20credible%20are%20the%20reasons%20for%20suspecting%20that%20these%20are%20frontmen%20for%20the%20Adani%20family%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EM.%20Damodaran%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20First%20of%20all%2C%20the%20report%20is%20very%20well-compiled.%20I%20think%20one%20must%20give%20credit%20to%20those%20that%20put%20it%20together.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20persuasive%20report.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20one%20that%20you%20can%20read%20and%20put%20aside%20because%20I%20think%20it%20raises%20interesting%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FF-_2-7Wgb_0%3Fsi%3DkqVN2nZpkBsMYHx0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20between%20being%20persuasive%20and%20being%20conclusive%2C%20there%20is%20an%20area%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20what%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20persons%20frontmen%3F%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20what%20happens%20in%20circumstantial%20evidence%20is%20you%20have%20to%20put%20everything%20together.%20No%20link%20must%20be%20weak.%20So%20every%20relationship%20that%20exists%20in%20this%20chain%20of%20relationships%20needs%20to%20be%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20they%20are%20frontmen%2C%20possible%20that%20there%20were%20transactions%20in%20shares%20made%20by%20funds%20that%20went%20out%20of%20India%2C%20which%20then%20makes%20it%20a%20case%20of%20round%20tripping.%20Clearly%20there%20are%20issues%20of%20whether%20the%2075%25%20limit%20that%20the%20promoters%20and%20promoter%20group%20can%20hold%20%E2%80%93%20has%20that%20been%20violated%20by%20resorting%20to%20this%20stratagem%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20issues%20that%20have%20been%20flagged%20in%20the%20report.%20Related%20party%20transactions%20(RPT)%2C%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20these%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20The%20report%20itself%2C%20I%20will%20not%20say%20is%20conclusive.%20It%20raises%20a%20number%20of%20issues.%20At%20best%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20presumption%20that%20some%20of%20this%20is%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20there%20a%20proof%20beyond%20doubt%20or%20is%20this%20preponderance%20of%20probability%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20the%20degree%20of%20proof%20that%20you%20need%3F%20These%20are%20the%20number%20of%20related%20questions%20you%20need%20to%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Would%20I%20be%20right%20in%20saying%20that%20you%20therefore%20believe%20that%20the%20issues%20raised%20need%20to%20be%20examined%20thoroughly%3F%20That%20the%20suspicions%20justify%20a%20thorough%20investigation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20say%20what%20the%20report%20has%20brought%20out%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated.%20It%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20brushed%20aside%2C%20not%20just%20because%20it%20concerns%20one%20big%20group%20in%20India%2C%20but%20to%20see%20whether%20there%20are%20systemic%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20plugged%20to%20ensure%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20(MPS)%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20case%20in%20which%20you%20can%20examine%20what%20are%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20people%20are%20getting%20around%20or%20can%20get%20around%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20several%20aspects%20that%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20into%20%E2%80%93%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20related%20party%20transactions.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20%5Binaudible%5D%20of%20disclosure.%20If%20some%20of%20this%20had%20happened%2C%20has%20it%20been%20disclosed%2C%20have%20the%20auditors%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20has%20the%20board%20looked%20at%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20that%20the%20board%20comprising%20several%20eminent%20persons%20would%2C%20after%20the%20report%20came%20out%20at%20least%2C%20have%20addressed%20some%20of%20these%20issues%20or%20looked%20into%20it%20or%20set%20in%20motion%20a%20kind%20of%20enquiry%20to%20determine%20whether%20this%20is%20right%20and%20actionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%2C%20Mr.%20Damodaran%2C%20put%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20points%20made%20in%20that%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20to%20you.%20The%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%2C%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20%5Bthe%5D%20documents%2C%20in%20January%202017%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%2C%20secretly%20controlled%20at%20least%2013%25%20of%20the%20free%20float%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20three%20out%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20four%20Adani%20companies%20listed%20on%20the%20stock%20exchange%20at%20that%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoesn%E2%80%99t%20this%20mean%20that%20if%20these%20men%20were%20fronts%20for%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20its%20shareholding%20will%20have%20substantially%20breached%20the%20SEBI%20regulation%20%E2%80%93%20that%2025%25%20of%20shares%20must%20be%20freely%20traded%20and%20in%20public%20hands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20this%20is%20established%20%E2%80%93%20at%20present%20and%20as%20you%20said%20in%20your%20introductory%20remarks%2C%20these%20are%20allegations%20%E2%80%93%20if%20this%20is%20established%2C%20then%20clearly%20there%20is%20some%20cause%20of%20action%20that%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20prove%20this%20or%20this%20cannot%20be%20proved%2C%20then%20I%20think%20we%20should%20not%20draw%20too%20many%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20important%20in%20my%20view%20is%20to%20note%20that%20SEBI%20has%20looked%20at%20all%20the%20points%20that%20they%20were%20expected%20to%20look%20at%20except%20two%2C%20and%20they%20are%20to%20file%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20already%20filed%20one%20which%20says%20we%20need%20a%20little%20more%20time%20to%20look%20at%20two%20of%20these%20because%20we%E2%80%99ve%20sought%20information%20from%20overseas%20regulators%2C%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20yet%2C%20and%20therefore%20we%20cannot%20put%20it%20all%20together%20and%20draw%20conclusions%20in%20your%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20would%20want%20to%20wait%20till%20SEBI%20puts%20this%20together%2C%20see%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20and%20what%20conclusions%20they%20draw%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20file%20it%20with%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20Now%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20take%20the%20example%20of%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20which%20is%20the%20flagship%20company.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20January%202017%20the%20promoters%20owned%2074.9%25%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20the%20free%20float%20should%20have%20been%2025.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20of%20that%2025.1%25%20free%20float%2C%2013.5%25%20was%20the%20Ahli-Chung%20stake.%20So%20if%20these%20two%20men%20were%20fronts%2C%20this%20presumably%20would%20prove%20that%20the%20flagship%20company%2C%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20was%20in%20flagrant%20breach%20of%20SEBI%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20SEBI%20is%20looking%20at%20it%20since%20this%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20all%20of%20us%20are%20looking%20at%20it%20and%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20not%20looking%20at%20it%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20unlikely%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20especially%20since%20they%20have%20to%20file%20a%20report%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20whether%20these%20are%20persons%20holding%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20promoters%20and%20therefore%20breaching%20the%2075%25%20limit%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20SEBI%20will%20certainly%20look%20at%2C%20and%20if%20there%20is%20a%20violation%2C%20there%20will%20be%20penal%20consequences%2C%20I%20have%20no%20doubt%20at%20all%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20question%20is%20that%20there%20are%20several%20other%20regulators%20involved.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20whole%20series%20of%20transactions%20and%20get%20beyond%20this%2C%20look%20at%20what%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20mentioned%20for%20example%2C%20you%20have%20issues%20of%20whether%20money%20has%20gone%20out%2C%20has%20it%20been%20brought%20back%2C%20is%20there%20round%20tripping%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20matter%20within%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20remit.%20That%20has%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20by%20some%20other%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%20or%20thereabouts%2C%20if%20memory%20serves%20me%20right%2C%20I%20recall%20reading%20about%20this%20that%20an%20appellate%20authority%20looking%20at%20the%20case%20made%20out%20by%20the%20DRI%20%5BDirectorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%5D%20had%20come%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20what%20was%20alleged%20was%20not%20established%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20in%20some%20sense%20%E2%80%93%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20closure%20was%20applied%2C%20but%20certainly%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20there%20was%20a%20plausible%20explanation%20given%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5Binaudible%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20is%20one%20element.%20RPT%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20If%20there%20are%20allegations%20that%20these%20are%20related%20parties%20and%20they%20have%20done%20transactions%2C%20you%20need%20to%20look%20at%20them%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20important.%20What%20is%20within%20SEBIs%20remit%20is%20clearly%20RPT%2C%20is%20clearly%20MPS%2C%20is%20clearly%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20transactions%20have%20been%20conducted%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20it%20is%20a%20work-in-progress%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-the-mention-of-an-adani-connection-trigger-the-modi-government%5C%22%3EDoes%20the%20Mention%20of%20an%20Adani%20Connection%20Trigger%20the%20Modi%20Government%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20reach%20the%20second%20issue%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20raises%3F%20If%20these%20are%20frontmen%20and%20if%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20transpires%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20the%20promoters%2C%20has%20exceeded%20SEBI%20stipulations%2C%20does%20that%20also%20then%20hint%20towards%20share%20price%20manipulation%3F%20Is%20that%20a%20legitimised%20suspicion%20to%20have%20in%20mind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20people%20that%20both%20OCCRP%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20spoken%20to%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20Indian%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20believe%20that%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20family%20has%20crossed%2075%25%2C%20then%20there%20%5Bare%5D%20clearly%20grounds%20to%20suspect%20share%20price%20manipulation.%20Would%20you%20agree%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20legitimate%20second%20suspicion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20move%20away%20from%20this%20particular%20case%20and%20look%20at%20why%20MPS%20exists.%20Twenty-five%20percent%20public%20shareholding%20of%20an%20entity%20that%20is%20listed%20in%20the%20securities%20market%20is%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20a%20method%20by%20which%20you%20can%20help%20to%20establish%20what%20should%20be%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20that%20is%20breached%2C%20if%20persons%20are%20investing%20in%20the%20stocks%2C%20if%20the%20promoter%20and%20the%20promoter%20group%20together%20hold%20more%20than%2075%25%2C%20clearly%20they%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20influence%20the%20prices.%20Because%20it%20is%20a%20very%20large%20chunk%2C%20above%2075%25%2C%20if%20you%20get%20to%2080-83%25%20to%20the%20numbers%20that%20you%20mentioned%2C%20would%20take%20it%20closer%20to%2085%25%20or%20even%20above%20that%20I%20imagine.%20Clearly%20you%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20the%20only%20group%20that%20has%20this%20situation%3F%20No.%20Several%20others%20also%20have%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20to%20the%20public.%20Government%20undertakings%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20exempt%20and%20therefore%20government%20continues%20as%20a%20majority%20shareholder%20and%20%5Bholds%5D%20above%2090%25%20in%20several%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20this%20lead%20automatically%3F%20%5Bsic%5D%20It%20can%20be%20an%20instrument.%20Has%20it%20happened%3F%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20So%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20simplifying%20it%20for%20the%20audience%20who%20may%20not%20be%20technically%20proficient%2C%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20the%20promoters%2C%20is%20in%20excess%20of%2075%25%2C%20then%20clearly%20there%20are%20grounds%20to%20suspect%20%E2%80%93%20only%20suspect%20%E2%80%93%20that%20there%20could%20be%20share%20price%20manipulation%2C%20and%20that%20is%20therefore%20something%20else%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Oh%2C%20clearly%20that%20is%20an%20aspect%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20into%2C%20because%20if%20you%20have%20a%20very%2C%20very%20large%20shareholding%20in%20the%20promoted%20group%2C%20clearly%20that%20can%20impact%20on%20share%20prices.%20Now%2C%20is%20that%20manipulation%2C%20are%20there%20things%20that%20are%20done%20in%20order%20to%20push%20prices%20up%2C%20and%20therefore%20you%20get%20other%20people%20to%20buy%20in%2C%20it%20gives%20the%20group%20much%20better%20numbers%20in%20the%20market.%20These%20are%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20as%20you%20said%20rightly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20suspicion%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20allegation%2C%20but%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20been%20put%20together%20well.%20I%20must%20say%20a%20lot%20of%20documents%20have%20been%20looked%20at%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20said%20at%20the%20outset%20%5Bthat%20it%20is%5D%20very%20persuasive.%20Is%20it%20conclusive%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20so%20sure%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20regulator%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESEBI%20headquarters%20in%20Mumbai.%20Photo%3A%20Jimmy%20Vikas%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20but%20the%20distance%2C%20as%20you%20said%2C%20between%20very%20persuasive%20and%20conclusive%2C%20is%20a%20distance%20that%20must%20be%20covered%20by%20investigation%20and%20that%20investigation%20has%20to%20be%20done%20by%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20correct%2C%20because%20if%20there%20is%20so%20much%20information%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20clearly%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation.%20I%20would%20go%20one%20step%20further%20and%20say%20that%20these%20investigations%20ought%20to%20be%20conducted%20quickly%2C%20so%20that%20confidence%20in%20the%20market%20is%20not%20adversely%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20second-guess%20the%20regulator%20on%20this.%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20seize%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20especially%20since%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20where%20they%20are%20to%20report%20back%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20saying%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20completed%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20let%20me%20remind%20you%20that%20a%20six-member%20committee%20of%20experts%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20had%20looked%20at%20some%20aspects%20of%20this%20%E2%80%93%20arising%20out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20brief%20that%20was%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20then%20concluded%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20regulator%20had%20been%20ignoring%20what%20it%20needed%20to%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20they%20went%20off%20on%20a%20tangent%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20to%20protect%20investors%2C%20what%20to%20do%20with%20people%20whose%20shares%20had%20been%20lost%2C%20all%20of%20which%20I%20think%20was%20completely%20unnecessary%20because%20it%20took%20the%20eye%20off%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20needed%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20principal%20requirement%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20them%20to%20look%20at%2C%20which%20was%20the%20regulator%20measuring%20up%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20report%20%E2%80%93%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20say%20it%20gives%20the%20regulator%20a%20clean%20chit%20%E2%80%93%20but%20certainly%20comes%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20evidence%20to%20show%20the%20regulator%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20now%2C%20actually%2C%20we%20have%20very%20good%20grounds%20given%20to%20us%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20given%20to%20us%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20well%2C%20and%20all%20of%20this%20put%20together%20for%20both%20papers%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20these%20are%20credible%20grounds%20for%20suspicion%20which%20require%20in-depth%2C%20honest%2C%20diligent%20and%20thorough%20investigation.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%2C%20we%20will%20be%20remiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20think%20we%20should%20not%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20and%20think%20that%20that%20is%20not%20being%20done%20%E2%80%93%20an%20honest%20diligent%2C%20investigation%20as%20you%20put%20it.%20The%20problem%20is%20some%20of%20this%20takes%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEspecially%20because%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20collect%20information%20from%20overseas%20regulators%2C%20and%20SEBI%20has%20said%20as%20much%20in%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20said%20that%20in%20these%20two%20cases%2C%20we%20need%20to%20get%20in%20from%20these%20two%20items%20in%20our%20inquiry%2C%20the%20others%20they%20have%20said%20our%20report%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20put%20to%20you%2C%20sir%2C%20two%20other%20facts%20before%20I%20move%20to%20something%20else%2C%20and%20ask%20you%20whether%20these%20two%20are%20the%20facts%20reported%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20grounds%20for%20believing%20this%20suspicion%20%E2%80%93%20that%20these%20two%20men%20are%20fronts%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20this%3A%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20these%20two%20men%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%2C%20made%20their%20investments%20in%20Adani%20companies%20through%20two%20funds.%20The%20two%20funds%20are%20the%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Fund%20and%20the%20EM%20Resurgent%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%2C%20%E2%80%9CBehind%20the%20scenes%2C%20all%20but%20two%20million%20dollars%20out%20of%20260%20million%20dollars%20in%20Adani%20stock%20held%20by%20the%20funds%20in%20September%202014%20were%20controlled%20by%20Ali%20and%20Chung%E2%80%99s%20companies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20question%20is%20this%2C%20is%20this%20huge%20and%20deliberate%20investment%20in%20Adani%20stock%20another%20reason%20for%20suspecting%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%20are%20frontmen%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20I%20think%20you%20need%20to%20also%20look%20at%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20not%20been%20addressed.%20How%20were%20these%20funds%20set%20up%3F%20Did%20these%20funds%20invite%20public%20investment%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20is%20it%20that%20was%20promised%3F%20Because%20there%20are%20funds%20that%20have%20significant%20investment%20in%20some%20companies%20and%20small%20investments%20in%20some%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20by%20itself%20is%20not%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20violative%20of%20any%20regulations%20unless%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20fund%20itself%20says%20that%20you%20should%20be%20widely%20dispersed%2C%20just%20the%20kind%20of%20directions%20you%20have%20for%20mutual%20funds%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20concentration%20beyond%20a%20certain%20level%20in%20a%20particular%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there%20are%20other%20regulators%20that%20also%20need%20to%20look%20at%20these.%20Overseas%20regulators%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20because%20I%20would%20imagine%20that%20information%20sharing%20under%20the%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20that%20IOSCO%20%5BInternational%20Organization%20of%20Securities%20Commissions%5D%20has%20should%20enable%20regulators%20to%20share%20information%20that%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20stability%20and%20growth%20of%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20SEBI%20seized%20of%20all%20of%20this.%20I%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20working%20it%20in%E2%80%A6%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20investigation%20is%20such%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20time-taking%20because%20they%20need%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20what%20they%20have%20told%20the%20court%20%E2%80%93%20to%20get%20information%20from%20outside%20regulators%20and%20that%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodi-adani-oligarchy-stock-offshore%5C%22%3EThe%20Undeniable%20Rise%20of%20Oligarchic%20Capitalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20put%20the%20second%20fact%20to%20you%2C%20again%20to%20ask%20whether%20the%20second%20fact%20corroborates%20the%20suspicion%20that%20these%20two%20men%20are%20fronts.%20According%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%E2%80%99s%20investments%20were%20overseen%20by%20an%20employee%20of%20Excel%20Investment%20and%20Advisory%20Services%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Vinod%20Adani%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Excel%20was%20paid%20an%20advisory%20fee%20related%20to%20these%20investments.%20In%20fact%2C%20OCCRP%20goes%20one%20step%20further%20%E2%80%93%20it%20says%20the%20agreement%20between%20Excel%20and%20the%20funds%20used%20by%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%20was%20signed%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20himself.%20Is%20that%20another%20reason%20for%20saying%20this%20suspicion%20that%20the%20two%20men%20are%20fronts%20is%20one%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20seriously%20investigated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20case%20that%20you%20can%20brush%20it%20aside%2C%20ignore%20it%2C%20turn%20a%20Nelson%E2%80%99s%20eye%E2%80%A6%20no%2C%20certainly%20not.%20But%20does%20that%20lead%20us%20to%20conclude%20that%20these%20were%20frontmen%2C%20that%20these%20were%20Vinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20persons%2C%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20had%20used%20them%20in%20order%20to%20invest%20money%20and%20that%20it%20was%20meant%20for%20violating%20the%20MPS%20etc.%3F%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20said%20rightly%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20elements%20in%20this%20report.%20Most%20of%20these%20elements%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20by%20someone%20who%20has%20both%20the%20responsibility%20as%20well%20as%20the%20skill%20sets%20to%20get%20to%20whatever%20is%20the%20truth.%20Until%20that%20emerges%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20and%20say%20this%20is%20open%20and%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%2C%20absolutely%20not.%20These%20are%20just%20suspicions%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah.%20Because%20it%E2%80%99s%20entirely%20possible%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20well-researched%20report%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that.%20But%20a%20well-researched%20report%20that%20throws%20up%20facts%20and%20information%2C%20it%20does%20not%20present%20a%20complete%20enough%20picture%20for%20an%20investigator%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98I%20got%20it%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20anything%20more%20to%20do%E2%80%99%2C%20or%20for%20a%20regulator%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98There%E2%80%99s%20no%20need%20for%20investigation%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20take%20this%20at%20face%20value%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20far%20from%20that.%20It%20casts%20a%20responsibility%20on%20them%20to%20investigate%20this%20quickly%2C%20thoroughly%2C%20honestly%2C%20diligently%20%E2%80%93%20I%20am%20using%20all%20the%20words%20that%20you%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20then%20ask%20you%20this%20question%2C%20and%20I%20do%20it%20because%20you%20are%20a%20former%20chairman%20of%20SEBI%20and%20someone%20who%20is%20a%20leading%20director%20in%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20companies.%20You%20have%20said%20clearly%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation%20and%20you%20added%20it%20must%20be%20done%20quickly.%20Then%20you%20said%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%20elements%2C%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20diligently%20and%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20confident%20are%20you%20that%20SEBI%20will%20do%20this%3F%20Both%20thoroughly%20and%20diligently%2C%20and%20in%20fairly%20quick%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20they%20will%20do%20it%20thoroughly%3B%20they%20will%20do%20it%20diligently.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20said%20this%20in%20an%20earlier%20interview%20with%20you%2C%20maybe%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20function%20of%20my%20growing%20years%2C%20but%20I%20tend%20to%20get%20impatient%20with%20the%20time%20taken%2C%20so%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20would%20want%20to%20see%20results%20quicker%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20also%20good%20for%20the%20system%2C%20but%20that%20said%2C%20they%20have%20to%20follow%20a%20process%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20leave%20any%20loose%20ends%20and%20therefore%20I%20think%20we%20must%20respect%20their%20judgment%20and%20trust%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20doing%20the%20right%20things%20in%20the%20right%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%5C%22%3EFresh%20Adani%20Revelations%20that%20Hint%20at%20Regulator%20SEBI%20Inaction%20Could%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20FATF%20Credibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20by%20that%20very%20carefully%20crafted%20answer%2C%20that%20the%20SEBI%20will%20do%20it%20diligently%20%5Band%5D%20thoroughly%2C%20but%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20so%20sure%20they%E2%80%99ll%20do%20it%20quickly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20beast.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20get%20information%20from%20various%20places%2C%20and%20unlike%20persons%20like%20me%20who%20are%20now%20outside%20the%20system%20%5Band%5D%20who%20can%20jump%20to%20conclusions%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20SEBI%20can%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20must%2C%20in%20these%20matters%2C%20build%20a%20watertight%20case%20that%20survives%20scrutiny%20at%20the%20appellate%20level%2C%20and%20perhaps%20it%20will%20even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20case%20against%20somebody%2C%20it%20travels%20right%20up%20to%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20where%20it%20will%20have%20to%20be%20defended.%20Therefore%2C%20all%20of%20that%20clearly%20will%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELet%20me%20tell%20you%20why%20some%20people%20have%20doubts%20not%20just%20about%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20SEBI%20will%20investigate%2C%20but%20also%20the%20diligence%20and%20the%20thoroughness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20the%20reason%3A%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20revealed%20and%20so%20did%20OCCRP%20as%20well%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20SEBI%2C%20as%20far%20back%20as%20January%202014%2C%20was%20informed%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20of%20fears%20of%20suspicious%20investment%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20SEBI%20did%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20SEBI%20may%20not%20have%20taken%20the%20tip-off%20seriously.%20And%20if%20that%20is%20true%2C%20would%20you%20accept%2C%20(a)%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20and%20(b)%20it%20will%20have%20damaged%20confidence%20in%20SEBI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%2C%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20jumped%20to%20conclusions%20and%20said%20that%20after%20getting%20that%20letter%20that%20we%20did%20nothing%20about%20it%20or%20buried%20the%20matter%20etc.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20any%20of%20us%20has%20any%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20interrupt%20you%20there%2C%20sir%3F%20Can%20I%20interrupt%20you%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah%2C%20please.%20Yeah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%20why%20I%20raised%20that%20question.%20In%20February%2C%20when%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20came%20out%2C%20I%20interviewed%20you.%20Roughly%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20maybe%20a%20week%20later%2C%20I%20interviewed%20Mr%20U.K.%20Sinha.%20Mr%20U.K.%20Sinha%20was%20chairman%20of%20SEBI%20from%202011%20to%202017%20and%20this%20letter%20of%20January%202014%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20was%20addressed%20to%20him%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20said%20to%20Mr%20Sinha%20in%20that%20interview%20that%20allegations%20about%20Adani%2C%20speculation%20and%20concerns%20about%20Adani%20existed%20long%20before%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20came%20out.%20That%20is%20one%20reason%20why%20Indian%20mutual%20funds%20have%20by%20and%20large%20avoided%20Adani%20Group%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20my%20question%20to%20Mr%20Sinha%20was%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20did%20SEBI%20not%20carry%20out%20its%20own%20investigation%3F%E2%80%99%20Long%20before%20Hindenburg%20happened%2C%20why%20did%20SEBI%20not%20do%20its%20own%20investigation%2C%20because%20these%20concerns%20were%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20in%20fact%20what%20Mr%20Sinha%20said%20to%20me%20in%20reply.%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20say%20that%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20information%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20round%20tripping%20happening%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20share%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20like%20this%2C%20according%20to%20my%20understanding%20and%20knowledge%2C%20that%20has%20come%20in%20public%20domain%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20revealing%20this%20letter%20from%20the%20DRI%20dated%20January%202014%20means%20it%20was%20known%20well%20before%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20and%20Mr%20Sinha%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20correct%20when%20he%20says%20it%20has%20come%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20for%20the%20first%20time%20with%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20people%20today%20ask%2C%20%E2%80%98Will%20SEBI%20be%20diligent%20and%20thorough%2C%20and%20will%20it%20be%20fast%20and%20quick%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20Mr.%20Sinha%20himself%20%E2%80%93%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20this%20in%20the%20newspapers%20%E2%80%93%20has%20said%20that%20the%20substance%20of%20that%20letter%20was%20also%20the%20substance%20of%20what%20DRI%20looked%20at%2C%20and%20the%20DRI%E2%80%99s%20appellate%20authority%20came%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20merit%20in%20the%20allegations%20for%20whatever%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20SEBI%20had%20done%20something.%20It%E2%80%99s%20likely%20that%20he%20would%20not%20want%20to%20reveal%20in%20public%20what%20happened%20by%20way%20of%20investigations%20%5Band%5D%20what%20was%20concluded%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20unfair%20expectation%3B%20to%20actually%20expect%20him%20to%20say%20all%20of%20this%20in%20public.%20And%20therefore%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20there%20was%20evidence%20of%20round%20tripping%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20round%20tripping%20is%20an%20offense%20that%20some%20other%20regulator%20ought%20to%20look%20at.%20Has%20that%20been%20established%20as%20of%20today%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_65PYAnyQXc%5C%22%3ENot%20Convinced%20by%20Hindenburg%20But%20Adani%20Claim%20of%20Attack%20on%20India%20Is%20Wrong%3A%20M%20Damodaran%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%E2%80%A6%20You%E2%80%99re%20absolutely%20right%20in%20one%20thing%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20that%20the%20DRI%20investigation%20after%20three%20years%20was%20called%20off%2C%20but%20the%20DRI%20was%20specifically%20investigating%20into%20siphoning%20off%20of%20money%20through%20overpricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5BThe%5D%20DRI%20was%20not%20investigating%20mysterious%20and%20unexplained%20investment%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20They%20were%20alerting%20SEBI%20to%20that%2C%20but%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20investigating%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20%5Bthe%5D%20DRI%20called%20off%20their%20investigation%20three%20years%20later%2C%20it%20was%20only%20to%20do%20with%20siphoning%20of%20money.%20The%20charge%20or%20the%20suspicion%20or%20the%20fear%20that%20inexplicable%20investment%20and%20disinvestments%20happening%20remains%2C%20and%20that%20is%20round%20tripping%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20and%20that%20is%20share%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClearly%20SEBI%20had%20been%20forewarned%20of%20these%20fears.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20they%20did%2C%20but%20for%20Mr%20Sinha%20to%20say%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20reason%20to%20believe%20this%20was%20happening%20before%20Hindenburg%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20correct.%20That%20was%20brought%20to%20their%20attention%20by%20%5Bthe%5D%20DRI%2C%20which%20is%20why%20I%20raised%20this%20question%20about%20whether%20SEBI%20will%20be%20upfront%2C%20transparent%20and%20diligent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20absolutely%20no%20doubt%20that%20it%20will%20be.%20It%20cannot%20afford%20not%20to%20be%2C%20and%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20credibility%20of%20a%20system%20and%20the%20people%20there%2C%20but%20also%20because%20if%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%2C%20every%20action%20of%20its%20would%20be%20a%20suspect%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20in%20relation%20to%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20I%20think%20both%20in%20enlightened%20self-interest%20as%20well%20as%20for%20maintaining%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20system%2C%20SEBI%20will%20do%20a%20thorough%20job.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20my%20only%20concern%20is%20the%20time%20that%20these%20processes%20take%20and%20I%20gave%20you%20a%20valid%20explanation%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20be%20a%20function%20of%20advancing%20years%20that%20you%20tend%20to%20get%20impatient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20add%2C%20impatience%20is%20a%20wonderful%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20question%2C%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20given%20that%20this%20story%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20done%20by%20OCCRP%20will%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20India%20as%20an%20investment%20destination%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20could%20affect%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20grow%20the%20Indian%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20there%20steps%20you%20believe%20the%20Indian%20government%20itself%20should%20take%20in%20response%20to%20what%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20put%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20the%20government%20would%20have%20seen%20the%20report.%20The%20government%20would%20have%20looked%20at%20what%20is%20actionable%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20government%2C%20what%20is%20actionable%20at%20the%20level%20of%20different%20regulators.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20all%20of%20that%20is%20something%20that%20is%20happening%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20let%20me%20also%20say%20this%2C%20that%20if%20there%20was%20such%20concern%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%2C%20that%20investors%20would%20have%20post%20the%20publication%20of%20this%20report%20%E2%80%93%20this%20report%E2%80%99s%20been%20around%20for%20some%20time%2C%20not%20that%20it%20happened%20yesterday%20only%20%E2%80%93%20you%20would%20have%20seen%20some%20impact%20of%20that%20by%20way%20of%20some%20funds%20moving%20out%20of%20India.%20Nothing%20of%20the%20kind%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20there%20have%20been%20significant%20investments%20in%20the%20market.%20There%20have%20been%20significant%20announcements%20regarding%20impending%20FDI.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20portfolio%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20foreign%20direct%20investment.%20And%20therefore%2C%20the%20confidence%20in%20the%20Indian%20system%20that%20India%20is%20in%20the%20vanguard%20of%20the%20growth%20economies%2C%20none%20of%20that%20will%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20these%20allegations%20will%20have%20to%20be%20investigated.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20my%20case%20that%20this%20has%20to%20be%20ignored%20%E2%80%93%20far%20from%20it.%20And%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20that%20somebody%20is%20working%20on%20it%20quietly%2C%20unseen%20by%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20thank%20you%20very%20much%20for%20agreeing%20to%20this%20interview.%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%20also%20for%20helping%20us%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20suspicions%20and%20allegations%20which%20are%20not%20conclusive%2C%20but%20as%20you%20said%2C%20they%20are%20very%20persuasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20you%20said%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20it%20diligently%20and%20thoroughly%20and%20relatively%20quickly.%20And%20you%E2%80%99re%20confident%20SEBI%20will%20do%20precisely%20that.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20hope%20your%20confidence%20is%20borne%20out.%20I%20thank%20you%20for%20this%20interview%2C%20take%20care%20sir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20thank%20you%20Karan.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranscribed%20by%20Karizma%20Ahmed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694758222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14190839%2FKT-12-B-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffull-text-former-sebi-chief-says-ft-occrp-adani-story-very-persuasive%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22M.%20Damodaran%20told%20Karan%20Thapar%20that%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20must%20investigate%20whether%20FT's%20%E2%80%98very%20persuasive%E2%80%99%20report%20is%20%E2%80%98conclusive%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20mustn't%20turn%20a%20%E2%80%98Nelson's%20eye%E2%80%99%20to%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffull-text-former-sebi-chief-says-ft-occrp-adani-story-very-persuasive%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Senior%20South%20Korea%2C%20US%20officials%20agree%20North%20Korea-Russia%20arms%20cooperation%20violates%20UN%20sanctions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694758216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103682648%2Cimgsize-59740.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsenior-south-korea-us-officials-agree-north-korea-russia-arms-cooperation-violates-un-sanctions%2Farticleshow%2F103682497.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103682497.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESenior%20diplomats%20and%20defense%20officials%20from%20South%20Korea%20and%20the%20United%20States%20have%20condemned%20military%20cooperation%20between%20North%20Korea%20and%20Russia%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20serious%20violation%20of%20UN%20sanctions.%20They%20have%20vowed%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20are%20consequences%20for%20this%20violation.%20The%20officials%20have%20urged%20Moscow%2C%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%20to%20take%20responsibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsenior-south-korea-us-officials-agree-north-korea-russia-arms-cooperation-violates-un-sanctions%2Farticleshow%2F103682497.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fsenior-south-korea-us-officials-agree-north-korea-russia-arms-cooperation-violates-un-