t.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20from%20Ferozepur%20Jhirka%20had%20approached%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20seeking%20protection%20from%20arrest.%20The%20hearing%20had%20been%20set%20for%20October%2019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fnuh-violence-congress-mla-mamman-khan-arrested-by-haryana-police-2435858-2023-09-14%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%C2%A0FIR%C2%A0No.149%20dated%20August%201%2C%202023%20registered%20under%20Sections%20148%2C%20149%2C%20153-A%2C%20379-A%2C%20436%2C%20506%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%20at%20Police%20Station%20Nagina%2C%20District%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana%3B%20there%20are%2052%20accused%20persons%20out%20of%20which%2042%20persons%20have%20been%20arrested.%20One%20Taufiq%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20in%20the%C2%A0FIR%C2%A0was%20arrested%20on%20August%209th%20and%20Taufiq%20named%20Mamman%20Khan%20as%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20this%20case.%20Thereafter%2C%20due%20investigation%20was%20conducted%20and%20the%20call%20details%20from%20the%20mobile%20phones%20and%20tower%20location%20of%20Taufiq%20and%20Mamman%20Khan%20were%20examined%20and%20it%20was%20found%20that%20calls%20were%20exchanged%20on%20July%2029th%20and%2030th%20%E2%80%93%20one%20day%20before%20July%2031st%20when%20the%20Nuh%20violence%20took%20place.%20As%20per%20the%20tower%20location%2C%20Mamman%20Khan%20was%20within%20an%20area%20of%201.5%20km%20from%20the%20place%20of%20occurrence%20on%20July%2029th%20and%2030th%20and%20thus%2C%20the%20averments%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20that%20he%20was%20not%20close%20to%20the%20place%20of%20the%20occurrence%20in%20the%20petition%20is%20not%20correct.%20Statements%20of%20Security%20Officers%20of%20the%20petitioner%20i.e.%2C%20Constable%20Jai%20Prakash%20and%20Constable%20Pradeep%20have%20also%20been%20recorded%20under%20Section%20161%20Cr.P.C.%20and%20the%20said%20two%20police%20officials%20have%20also%20confirmed%20the%20fact%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20Mamman%20Khan%20being%20within%20a%20range%20of%201.5%20km%20from%20the%20place%20of%20occurrence%20on%20July%2029th%20and%2030th.%20Also%2C%20Mamman%20Khan%20had%20posted%20on%20Whatsapp%20as%20well%20as%20on%C2%A0Facebook%20on%20July%2030th%20that%20%E2%80%98Nobody%20needs%20to%20worry%20as%20the%20petitioner%20had%20fought%20for%20them%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20and%20will%20fight%20for%20them%20in%20Mewat%20also.%E2%80%99%20It%20is%20further%20submitted%20that%20one%20Abdulla%20Khan%20is%20also%20an%20accused%20who%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20arrested%20and%20even%20in%20one%20of%20his%20posts%2C%20he%20had%20mentioned%20%E2%80%9CEngineer%20Mamman%20Khan%20MLA%20Mission%20complete%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20stated%20that%20Khan%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20join%20the%20investigation%20on%20August%2025%2C%20and%20on%20August%2031%20he%20had%20asked%20for%20ten%20days%E2%80%99%20time%20as%20he%20was%20not%20feeling%20well.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20claimed%2C%20he%20did%20not%20join%20after%20that%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhan%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20MLA%20had%20not%20been%20told%20that%20he%20was%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR.%20The%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fact%20that%20the%20petitioner%20has%20been%20nominated%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%C2%A0has%20been%20made%20known%20to%20the%20petitioner%20today%20itself%2C%20thus%2C%20the%20petitioner%20be%20given%20liberty%20to%20seek%20appropriate%20remedy%20for%20protection%20of%20liberty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694748330000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15085402%2FOEqrE5jw_400x400.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcongress-mla-mamman-khan-arrested-in-nuh-vi