companies%2Fnews%2Fjet-airways-founder-goyal-sent-to-14-day-custody-in-bank-fraud-case-123091400356_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20Criticises%20Modi's%20'Celebrations'%20on%20Day%203%20Officers%20Were%20Killed%20in%20Kashmir%20Militant%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14225747%2Fimage-1315.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20lashed%20out%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20participating%20in%20celebrations%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20office%2C%20hailing%20his%20successful%20leadership%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20on%20a%20day%20when%20three%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3Ewere%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20militant%20attack%20in%20south%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%2C%20the%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%2C%20Colonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%2C%20based%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kokernag%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsouth-kashmir-officers-killed-attack%5C%22%3Ekilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20(DSP)%2C%20Humayun%20Muzamil%20Bhat%2C%20and%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20of%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Modi%20received%20a%20grand%20welcome%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%20where%20party%20workers%20gathered%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20congratulate%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20conducting%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Modi%20was%20showered%20with%20flower%20petals%2C%20as%20he%20took%20a%20victory%20lap%20around%20the%20BJP%20office%20and%20met%20party%20workers%20who%20offered%20him%20flowers%20and%20congratulated%20him%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2014)%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Congress%20Ex-Servicemen%20Department%2C%20Colonel%20Rohit%20Chaudhary%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20is%20very%20disheartening%20and%20painful%20to%20note%20that%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20ji%20has%20shown%20utter%20disrespect%20and%20insensitivity%20towards%20the%20sacrifices%20made%20by%20our%20brave%20soldiers.%20While%20our%20soldiers%20(were)%20fighting%20the%20battle%20with%20Pakistan-sponsored%20terrorists%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20and%20news%20had%20come%20out%20about%20the%20death%20of%20our%20three%20soldiers%20and%20some%20were%20wounded%2C%20but%20Modi%20ji%20was%20doing%20his%20own%20Mahima%20Mandan%20in%20his%20own%20BJP%20headquarters%20by%20his%20own%20BJP%20people%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20showering%20flowers%20on%20him%20and%20Modi%20ji%20was%20projecting%20his%20grandeur%20image%20in%20front%20of%20the%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20families%20of%20the%20soldiers%20are%20grieving%2C%20the%20entire%20nation%20was%20shocked%20with%20the%20sad%20news.%20The%20Indian%20Army%20was%20continuing%20its%20cordon%20and%20search%20operations%20in%20the%20hot%20bed%20area%20of%20the%20militancy%20but%20the%20BJP%20cadres%20continued%20their%20celebration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20also%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20celebration%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20and%20asked%20why%20Modi%20could%20not%20postpone%20the%20celebration%20by%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20utterly%20shocking%20is%20that%20PM%20Modi%20chose%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccelebrate%20himself%20for%20G20%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20BJP%20HQ%20yesterday%20with%20a%20grand%20party%20AFTER%20these%20bravehearts%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20%26amp%3B%20the%20news%20was%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EModi%20shamelessly%20celebrates%20while%20our%20bravehearts%20lay%20down%20their%20lives%20%F0%9F%91%87%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYesterday%20our%20bravehearts%20DySP%20Humayan%20Bhat%2C%20Maj%20Ashish%20Dhonack%2C%20%26amp%3B%20Col%20Manpreet%20Singh%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20while%20combating%20terrorists%20in%20Anantnag%2C%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20nation%20is%20eternally%20indebted%20to%20them%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Saket%20Gokhale%20(%40SaketGokhale)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSaketGokhale%2Fstatus%2F1702162149886550122%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCouldn%E2%80%99t%20Modi%20postpone%20his%20self%20PR%20for%20just%201%20day%3F%20Did%20BJP%20have%20to%20celebrate%20%26amp%3B%20glorify%20Modi%20when%20such%20a%20tragedy%20has%20occurred%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20on%20why%20the%20celebrations%20could%20not%20be%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20BJP%20should%20tell%20the%20country%20what%20was%20such%20an%20important%20%E2%80%98celebration%E2%80%99%20that%20could%20not%20be%20postponed%20for%20two%20days%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20supreme%20dedication%20of%20the%20officers%20and%20soldiers%20of%20our%20armed%20forces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9Cexpected%20more%20sensitivity%2C%20especially%20on%20a%20day%20when%20our%20security%20forces%20have%20fought%20a%20fierce%20fight%20with%20militants%20in%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20could%20have%20been%20postponed%2C%20expected%20more%20sensitivity%2C%20especially%20on%20a%20day%20when%20our%20security%20forces%20have%20fought%20a%20fierce%20fight%20with%20militants%20in%20Kashmir.%20Already%20three%20of%20our%20brave%20men%20have%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20while%20more%20injuries%20reported.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3SLTXSOqa1%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3SLTXSOqa1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40priyankac19)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpriyankac19%2Fstatus%2F1701983608972705904%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said%20that%20when%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfuneral%20procession%20of%20our%20martyrs%20were%20being%20carried%20out%2C%20Modi%20was%20celebrating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20(Modi)%20had%20promised%20that%20you%20would%20end%20terrorism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20soldiers%20were%20martyred%20in%20Pulwama%2C%20Modi%20was%20busy%20shooting%20a%20show%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20When%20dead%20bodies%20were%20floating%20on%20the%20Ganges%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20Modi%20was%20campaigning%20in%20Bengal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20give%20a%20befitting%20response%20to%20Pakistan-sponsored%20terrorism.%20AAP%20will%20raise%20this%20issue%20in%20the%20upcoming%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20while%20he%20and%20Raghav%20Chadha%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%2C%20other%20AAP%20MPs%20will%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2019-pm-narendra-modi-was-busy-with-film-shoot-when-nation-was-mourning-pulwama-1996996%5C%22%3Ehas%20earlier%20faced%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%20for%20allegedly%20shooting%20a%20show%20at%20the%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%20when%20the%20Pulwama%20terror%20attack%20took%20place%20in%20which%20over%2040%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20BJP%20parliamentary%20board%20on%20Wednesday%20passed%20a%20resolution%20hailing%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20at%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20note%20with%20great%20pride%20the%20impeccable%20leadership%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20showcased%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20at%20the%20summit.%20The%20G20%20Delhi%20summit%20stands%20as%20a%20monumental%20chapter%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20annals%2C%20marking%20a%20transformative%20moment%20in%20how%20our%20nation%20is%20perceived%20and%20engaged%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20also%20passed%20a%20resolution%20hailing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G20%20Summit%2C%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20(cabinet)%20recognised%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20giving%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%20a%20strong%20direction%20with%20a%20view%20to%20promoting%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1957163%5C%22%3Ecabinet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694712727000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14225747%2Fimage-1315.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpol