20books%20and%20courses.%20Their%20awareness%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20piracy%20grew%20when%20they%20saw%20a%20close%20friend%20affected%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20roommate%20Satish%20used%20to%20teach%20chemistry%20to%20Class%2011%20and%2012%20students%20in%20Mathura%20and%20Delhi%20every%20weekend%20for%20a%20year.%20When%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301984%2Fjamtara-girl-ranks-upsc-cse-by-learning-from-youtube-videos-no-coaching-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20online%20coaching%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20popular%2C%20he%20thought%20of%20transitioning%20his%20classes%20online.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20sharing%20his%20carefully%20crafted%20notes%20online%2C%20fearing%20that%20his%20content%20might%20be%20leaked%20and%20distributed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatish%E2%80%99s%20quandary%20led%20the%20two%20friends%20to%20realise%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20that%20online%20video%20piracy%20was%20adversely%20affecting%20teachers%20like%20Satish%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20upload%20good%20content%20online.%20Many%20individuals%20would%20download%20these%20class%20videos%20and%20distribute%20them%20on%20platforms%20like%20Telegram%2C%20YouTube%20or%20WhatsApp%2C%20reaching%20a%20large%20audience.%20This%20situation%20resulted%20in%20genuine%20teachers%20losing%20the%20opportunity%20to%20enrol%20new%20students%20and%20losing%20income%20as%20a%20consequence%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20piracy%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20harm%20movie%20and%20show%20producers%3B%20it%20also%20impacts%20teachers%20and%20creators%20of%20educational%20content.%20Ultimately%20if%20teachers%20do%20not%20put%20their%20best%20content%20out%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20it%20is%20a%20loss%20to%20the%20student%20community%20as%20well.%20According%20to%20a%202022%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EAnkura%20Piracy%20Statistics%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20India%20ranks%20as%20the%20third-largest%20contributor%20to%20visits%20to%20content%20piracy%20websites%2C%20following%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%2C%20with%20over%20seven%20billion%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20while%20they%20were%20still%20students%2C%20these%20two%20engineers%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20solve%20this%20issue%20using%20their%20video%20encryption%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20security%20against%20online%20piracy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vibhav%20Sinha%20and%20Siddhant%20Jain%20founded%20VdoCipher%20in%202014%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-founders-1694680977-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329867%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVibhav%20Sinha%20and%20Siddhant%20Jain%20founded%20VdoCipher%20in%202014.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249463%2Fsridhar-vembu-zoho-tech-entrepreneur-billionaire-padmashri-rural-migration-infrastructure-software-development-coding-indian-villages-silicon-valley-america-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencryption%20and%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Vibhav%20decided%20to%20combine%20encryption%20with%20cloud-based%20video%20players.%20Siddhant%20joined%20him%20to%20test%20the%20product%20and%20help%20with%20the%20sales.%20They%20first%20piloted%20their%20prototype%20with%20a%20finance-based%20e-learning%20platform%2C%20and%20after%20some%20tweaks%2C%20launched%20VdoCipher%20in%20September%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVdoCipher%20provides%20highly%20secure%20DRM%20(Digital%20Rights%20Management)%20encryption%20%E2%80%94%20a%20security%20that%20protects%20videos%20from%20unauthorised%20access%20%E2%80%94%20and%20user-based%20watermarking.%20This%20is%20combined%20with%20a%20smart%20customisable%20video%20player%20to%20ensure%20that%20videos%20are%20not%20illegally%20downloaded%2C%20and%20that%20viewers%20have%20a%20great%20playback%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20security%20through%20DRM%20encryption%20and%20watermarking.%20Basically%2C%20any%20customer%2C%20be%20it%20a%20teacher%20or%20an%20ed-tech%20platform%2C%20is%20provided%20with%20a%20video%20dashboard.%20They%20upload%20the%20content%20to%20that%20dashboard%20where%20it%20is%20encrypted%2C%20ensuring%20access%20only%20to%20authorised%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Siddhant%2C%20CEO%2C%20VdoCipher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20mobile%20phones%2C%20we%20can%20prevent%20screen%20capture%20also.%20Since%20this%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20prevented%20on%20computers%20in%20all%20cases%2C%20we%20provide%20user-based%20watermarking%20to%20discourage%20sharing.%20If%20they%20choose%20to%20share%20the%20screenshot%2C%20their%20name%2Fuser%20ID%20will%20appear%20on%20the%20image%3B%20it%20also%20helps%20us%20trace%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20duo%20claim%20to%20offer%20%E2%80%98Hollywood%20grade%20security%E2%80%99%20as%20they%20use%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20by%20Netflix%20and%20other%20large%20streaming%20services.%20Their%20USP%20is%20also%20their%20ability%20to%20provide%20this%20anti-piracy%20technology%20to%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20small%20teacher%20taking%20an%20online%20class%20to%20large%20ed-tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20Google%20DRM%20encryption%20and%20Apple%20DRM%20encryption%2C%20which%20provide%20very%20high%20security.%20They%20are%20the%20tools%20used%20by%20Netflix%2C%20Hollywood%20and%20Bollywood%20movies.%20We%20were%20the%20first%20company%20in%20India%20to%20provide%20such%20a%20high%20level%20of%20security%20technology%20in%20an%20easy-to-use%20way%2C%20notes%20Siddhant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20tech%20was%20not%20available%20to%20e-learning%20platforms%20as%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20integrate.%20We%20have%20made%20it%20easy%20and%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20government%20exam%20preparation%20course%20platform%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294819%2Futtar-pradesh-siblings-clear-upsc-cse-join-as-ias-ips-officers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E(UPSC%20and%20others)%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20over%2010%2C000%20online%20students%20and%2017%20centres%20across%20the%20country%20adds%20that%20their%20videos%20were%20getting%20leaked%20as%20the%20streaming%20platform%20was%20not%20secure.%C2%A0In%202019%2C%20they%20started%20using%20VdoCipher%E2%80%99s%20service%20and%20saw%20a%20marked%20difference%2C%20with%20more%20teachers%20trusting%20them.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CPartnering%20with%20VdoCipher%20stopped%20video%20sharing%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20brand%20building%20too.%20Teachers%20also%20developed%20confidence%20in%20our%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20security%2C%20VdoCipher%20also%20provides%20smooth%20streaming%20for%20slow%20internet%20connections%2C%20which%20helps%20premium%20content%20reach%20students%20in%20Tier%20II%20and%20III%20cities.%20VdoCipher%20also%20enables%20offline%20playback%20on%20mobiles%20and%20a%20bunch%20of%20interactive%20player%20features%20to%20ensure%20the%20best%20student%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20students%20from%20any%20remote%20areas%20in%20our%20country%20should%20get%20access%20to%20premium%20video%20content.%20Poor%20network%20connectivity%20should%20not%20be%20a%20hindrance%20in%20accessing%20quality%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVdoCipher%20uses%20a%20usage-based%20pricing%20model%20where%20customers%20pay%20based%20on%20how%20much%20data%20their%20students%20or%20viewers%20use.%20The%20duo%20claims%20to%20have%20over%203%2C000%20paying%20customers%20across%20100%20countries%2C%20streaming%20over%20seven%20million%20hours%20of%20content%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis.%20They%20say%20that%20as%20COVID%20led%20to%20a%20boom%20in%20the%20ed-tech%20space%2C%20the%20need%20for%20content%20security%20is%20also%20booming.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20seen%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20student%20footfall.%20This%20security%20has%20helped%20us%20do%20justice%20to%20serious%20students%2C%20teachers%20and%20other%20business%20stakeholders%20who%20were%20putting%20efforts%20in%20terms%20of%20time%20and%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20teachers%20protect%20their%20content%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fvdocipher-team-min-1694681425.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22VdoCipher%20helps%20educators%20fight%20video%20piracy%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c