experience%20crop%20losses.%20For%20this%2C%20%3Cem%3Epatwari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(village%20registrar)%20is%20appointed%20to%20survey%20the%20damage.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20seek%20a%20share%20in%20the%20compensation%20amount.%20If%20somebody%20refuses%20to%20give%20the%20amount%2C%20they%20remove%20their%20names%20from%20the%20list.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20says%20he%20was%20able%20to%20highlight%20these%20challenges%20in%20front%20of%20IAS%20trainees%20at%20LBSNAA.%20He%20also%20advised%20them%20to%20not%20rely%20on%20junior%20officers%20only%2C%20and%20to%20visit%20farmers%E2%80%99%20sites%20on%20their%20own%20to%20understand%20the%20challenges%20at%20the%20grassroots%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20progress%20with%20farming%20alone.%20After%20sowing%2C%20it%20takes%20five%20months%20to%20generate%20income%20from%20the%20crop.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20they%20are%20left%20without%20any%20means%20to%20earn.%20So%2C%20officers%20should%20encourage%20farmers%20to%20adopt%20parallel%20businesses%20like%20poultry%20farming%2C%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20silk%20and%20cattle%20rearing%2C%20and%20vermicompost%20business%20to%20boost%20their%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavindra%20shares%20that%20it%20was%20crucial%20for%20him%20to%20put%20forward%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20expectations%20to%20these%20future%20officers%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20received%20this%20opportunity%20felt%20like%20a%20great%20achievement.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20LBSNAA%2C%20reputed%20officers%20lecture%20the%20IAS%20trainees.%20And%20that%20day%2C%20a%20farmer%20was%20able%20to%20take%20the%20stage.%20I%20hope%20with%20my%20work%2C%20younger%20generations%20do%20not%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20seek%20a%20career%20in%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Ravindra%20Metkar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694613032000%2C%