g%20up%20there%2C%20the%20young%20girl%20gained%20insight%20into%20the%20challenging%20lives%20of%20farmers%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20she%20learned%20two%20important%20lessons%20from%20her%20father.%20One%20%E2%80%94%20the%20importance%20of%20millets%3B%20two%20%E2%80%94%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98corporate%20social%20responsibility%E2%80%99%20even%20before%20she%20had%20heard%20the%20term%20CSR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20studied%20in%20a%20Marathi%20medium%20school%20where%20most%20of%20the%20children%20faced%20several%20hardships.%20Their%20fathers%20were%20farmers%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20steady%20income%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20The%20girls%20were%20married%20early%20and%20weren%E2%80%99t%20given%20access%20to%20higher%20education.%20Most%20women%20in%20my%20orthodox%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%20%3C%2Fem%3Efamily%20also%20faced%20similar%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20including%20being%20forced%20to%20wear%20%3Cem%3Eghungats%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20cloth%20to%20cover%20the%20head)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20stories%20of%20harassment%20and%20domestic%20violence%20from%20schoolmates%20and%20relatives%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20lawyer%20to%20help%20women%20facing%20such%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20a%20different%20life%20than%20my%20mother%2C%20sisters%2C%20or%20sisters-in-law.%20I%20had%20witnessed%20my%20near%20and%20dear%20ones%20fall%20victim%20to%20domestic%20violence.%20Girls%20in%20my%20school%20were%20denied%20education%20and%20married%20early.%20So%2C%20I%20fought%20for%20my%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharmila%20now%20considers%20herself%20lucky%20because%20both%20her%20father%20and%20later%20her%20husband%20prioritised%20her%20education.%20However%2C%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20the%20farming%20community%20that%20she%20witnessed%20growing%20up%2C%20such%20as%20failing%20crops%20and%20increasing%20debts%2C%20deeply%20affected%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20through%20close%20quarters%20what%20a%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%20go%20through%20when%20their%20crop%20fails%2C%20or%20when%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20rain.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20finding%20solutions%20for%20these%20problems%2C%20as%20the%20water%20crisis%20was%20only%20increasing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20challenges%20inspired%20her%20to%20get%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20environmental%20and%20agricultural%20law%20in%20England%20after%20getting%20married.%20She%20worked%20in%20the%20UK%20from%201997%20to%201999%20and%20later%20moved%20to%20Canada%2C%20where%20she%20practised%20until%202007.%20Afterwards%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20her%20homeland%20in%20response%20to%20the%20difficulties%20faced%20by%20Indian%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20farmers%20switch%20to%20sustainable%20methods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sharmila%20is%20a%20social%20entreprenuer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-300x244.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-500x406.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-768x624.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsharmila-2-1694440857-150x122.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329600%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22