ing%20water%20needs.%20However%2C%20the%20local%20suppliers%20of%20these%20cans%20would%20often%20deliver%20dirty%20or%20cloudy%20cans%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mother%20of%20two%20children%20aged%2011%20and%209%2C%20she%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20she%20offered%20her%20children%20to%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20forced%20to%20fulfill%20our%20daily%20drinking%20needs%20from%20these%20cans%20as%20the%20tap%20water%20here%20is%20not%20clean.%20But%20whether%20I%20will%20be%20supplied%20with%20a%20clean%20can%20or%20a%20bad%20one%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20stock%20that%20the%20shopkeeper%20receives%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2040-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFed%20up%20with%20this%20situation%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20went%20to%20the%20spot%20where%20these%20water%20cans%20were%20unloaded.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20all%20the%20cans%20were%20irresponsibly%20thrown%20around.%20Chennai%20is%20a%20very%20hot%20place.%20When%20plastic%20cans%20are%20left%20outside%20in%20the%20heat%2C%20they%20go%20bad%20making%20the%20water%2C%20or%20any%20content%2C%20unfit%20for%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20six%20months%20back%2C%20upon%20her%20friend%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%2C%20she%20switched%20to%20using%20water%20cans%20by%20%E2%80%98BookWater%E2%80%99.%20The%20company%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20IoT%20(Internet%20of%20Things)-powered%20and%20quality-based%20water%20delivery%20platform%20in%20the%20world%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20scan%20the%20QR%20code%20on%20its%20water%20cans%20and%20get%20details%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20cans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fbookwater-1694173006.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%