20Indian%20actors%20in%20Hollywood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Heroines%20of%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%20(1947%E2%80%931971)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20organised%20themselves%20into%20a%20group%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Mukti%20Bahini%E2%80%99.%20They%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20young%20women%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20combat%20and%20various%20operations.%20Two%20of%20its%20members%20Captain%20Sitara%20Begum%20and%20Taramon%20Bibi%20were%20conferred%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Bir%20Protik%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fourth%20highest%20gallantry%20award%20in%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%94%20for%20their%20outstanding%20bravery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaramon%20Bibi%20worked%20as%20a%20cook%20for%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%20and%20never%20missed%20a%20chance%20to%20use%20this%20position%20of%20hers%20to%20roam%20through%20the%20area%20and%20keep%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324744%2Fmany-nayak-historic-film-on-caste-kahi-debe-sandesh-created-chhatisgarhi-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20of%20happenings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20did%20this%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20mental%20disability.%20She%20would%20observe%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20then%20report%20these%20to%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%2C%20who%20would%20then%20act%20on%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Sitara%20Begum%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20force.%20The%20Kolkata%20native%20oversaw%20operations%20at%20a%20Bangladesh%20Hospital%20where%20casualties%20of%20war%20and%20emergent%20cases%20needed%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20these%20two%20fearless%20women%20could%20play%20their%20role%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20Rajkumari%20Gupta%20displayed%20the%20same%20zeal%20during%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324194%2Fkishori-mohan-bandyopadhyay-worked-with-ronald-ross-malaria-research-nobel-prize-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20Madan%20Mohan%20Gupta%20joined%20the%20Independence%20movement%20where%20they%20would%20deliver%20secret%20messages%20to%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20times%2C%20Gupta%20put%20her%20life%20on%20the%20line%20while%20delivering%20guns%20to%20the%20revolutionaries.%20She%20once%20famously%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHum%20upar%20se%20Gandhivaadi%20the%2C%20neeche%20se%20krantivaadi%20the%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(We%20were%20Gandhians%20from%20above%3B%20underneath%20we%20were%20revolutionaries).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Breaking%20stereotypes%20through%20literature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20and%20their%20pragmatic%20approaches%20to%20dealing%20with%20crisis%20situations%20have%20gone%20down%20in%20history.%20For%20instance%2C%20Dr%20Gangubai%20Hangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20taboo%20for%20women%20to%20take%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307227%2Fsitar-makers-of-miraj-handcraft-tanpura-veena-for-musicians-artisans-music-industry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20not%20only%20did%20it%20but%20excelled%2C%20going%20on%20to%20win%20the%20Sangeet%20Natak%20Akademi%20Award%20(1973)%2C%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20(1971)%20and%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20(2002).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20the%20chosen%20one%20to%20sing%20the%20welcome%20song%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20session%20in%20Belagavi%20in%201924.%20The%20audience%20comprising%20Gandhi%